642511,128,509,71,98,1,207,22,"Evaṃ tattha tattha dānamayaṃ puññasambhāraṃ karonto itarañca nibbānatthaṃ sambharanto devamanussesu saṃsaritvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthinagare rañño pasenadissa amaccakule nibbatti,‘‘ vīro’’ tissa nāmaṃ akaṃsu. "
