642580,128,549,49,70,1,117,17,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yaṃ bhagavato santike mamāgamanaṃ, yaṃ vā mayā tattha āgataṃ, taṃ svāgataṃ, svāgatattāyeva na durāgataṃ. "
