642716,128,606,11,22,1,88,11,So kira atthadassino bhagavato kāle kacchapayoniyaṃ nibbatto vinatāya nāma nadiyā vasati. 
642717,128,606,23,27,1,41,4,Tassa khuddakanāvappamāṇo attabhāvo ahosi. 
642718,128,606,28,53,1,140,19,"So kira ekadivasaṃ bhagavantaṃ nadiyā tīre ṭhitaṃ disvā,‘‘ pāraṃ gantukāmo maññe bhagavā’’ ti attano piṭṭhiyaṃ āropetvā netukāmo pādamūle nipajji. "
