642834,128,656,216,238,1,180,21,Tassa yāvatatiyaṃ kathentassāpi itaro thero kathaṃ asaddahitvā attanā diṭṭhakāraṇaṃyeva bhūtattaṃ katvā gaṇhanto tena saddhiṃ ekamaggena agantvā aññena maggena satthu santikaṃ gato. 
642835,128,656,239,246,1,55,7,Itaropi bhikkhu aññena maggena satthu santikaṃyeva gato. 
642836,128,657,2,33,1,215,25,"Tato bhikkhusaṅghassa uposathāgāraṃ pavisanavelāya so bhikkhu taṃ bhikkhuṃ uposathagge sañjānitvā,‘‘ imasmiṃ uposathagge evarūpo nāma pāpabhikkhu atthi, nāhaṃ tena saddhiṃ uposathaṃ karissāmī’’ ti nikkhamitvā bahi aṭṭhāsi. "
642837,128,657,34,63,1,138,19,"Atha bhummadevatā‘‘ bhāriyaṃ mayā kammaṃ katan’’ ti mahallakaupāsakavaṇṇena tassa santikaṃ gantvā‘‘ kasmā, bhante, ayyo imasmiṃ ṭhāne ṭhito’’ ti āha."
642838,128,657,64,88,1,106,15,"‘‘ Upāsaka, imaṃ uposathaggaṃ eko pāpabhikkhu paviṭṭho,‘ nāhaṃ tena saddhiṃ uposathaṃ karomī’ ti bahi ṭhitomhī’’ ti."
