643371,128,915,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
643372,128,915,14,41,1,242,27,So kira ito ekanavute kappe vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ passitvā pasannamānaso nānāpupphehi pūjetvā tena puññakammena devaloke nibbatto puna aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto kassapassa bhagavato sāsane pabbajitvā samaṇadhammaṃ karoti. 
643373,128,915,42,54,1,123,12,Tena ca samayena satthārā bhaddekarattapaṭipadāya kathitāya aññataro bhikkhu bhaddekarattasuttavasena tena sākacchaṃ karoti. 
643374,128,915,55,59,1,19,4,So taṃ na sampāyāsi. 
