643557,128,994,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
643558,128,994,12,32,1,186,19,"So kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā araññāyatane vasanto tattha bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso phalāphalaṃ adāsi, tathā bhikkhusaṅghassa. "
643559,128,994,33,52,1,203,19,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto kassapassa sammāsambuddhassa kāle khattiyakule nibbattitvā anukkamena viññutaṃ patto kalyāṇamittasannissayena laddhasaṃvego sāsane pabbajitvā bahussuto ahosi. 
643560,128,994,53,62,1,68,9,Jātimadena sutamadena ca attānaṃ ukkaṃsento pare ca vambhento vihāsi. 
643561,128,994,63,74,1,100,10,So imasmiṃ buddhuppāde tassa kammassa nissandena sāvatthiyaṃ paribhūtarūpe susānagopakakule nibbatti. 
643562,128,994,75,79,1,25,4,Suppiyo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. 
643563,128,994,80,105,1,183,20,Atha viññutaṃ patto attano sahāyabhūtaṃ sopākattheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā tassa santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaṃvego pabbajitvā sammāpaṭipattiṃ pūretvā‘‘ ajaraṃ jīramānenā’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
643564,128,995,2,12,1,48,6,"32. Tattha ajaran ti jarārahitaṃ, nibbānaṃ sandhāyāha. "
643565,128,995,13,28,1,105,14,"Tañhi ajātattā natthi ettha jarā, etasmiṃ vā adhigate puggalassa sā natthīti jarābhāvahetutopi ajaraṃ nāma. "
643566,128,995,29,37,1,52,6,"{Jīramānenā}ti jīrantena, khaṇe khaṇe jaraṃ pāpuṇantena. "
643567,128,995,38,47,1,66,6,"{Tappamānenā}ti santappamānena, rāgādīhi ekādasahi aggīhi dayhamānena. "
643568,128,995,48,53,1,61,5,Nibbutin ti yathāvuttasantāpābhāvato nibbutasabhāvaṃ nibbānaṃ. 
643569,128,995,54,58,1,35,4,Nimiyan ti parivatteyyaṃ cetāpeyyaṃ. 
643570,128,995,59,65,1,85,6,Paramaṃ santin ti anavasesakilesābhisaṅkhārapariḷāhavūpasamadhammatāya uttamaṃ santiṃ. 
643571,128,995,66,70,1,40,4,Catūhi yogehi ananubandhattā yogakkhemaṃ. 
643572,128,995,71,76,1,47,5,Attano uttaritarassa kassaci abhāvato anuttaraṃ. 
643573,128,995,77,119,1,336,35,"Ayañhettha saṅkhepattho– khaṇe khaṇe jarāya abhibhuyyamānattā jīramānena, tathā rāgaggiādīhi santappamānena gato evaṃ aniccena dukkhena asārena sabbathāpi anupasantasabhāvena saupaddavena, tappaṭipakkhabhāvato ajaraṃ paramupasamabhūtaṃ kenaci anupaddutaṃ anuttaraṃ nibbānaṃ nimiyaṃ parivatteyyaṃ‘‘ mahā vata me lābho mahā udayo hatthagato’’ ti. "
643574,128,995,120,166,1,326,38,"Yathā hi manussā yaṃ kiñci bhaṇḍaṃ parivattentā nirapekkhā gayhamānena sambahumānā honti, evamayaṃ thero pahitatto viharanto attano kāye ca jīvite ca nirapekkhataṃ, nibbānaṃ paṭipesitattañca pakāsento‘‘ nimiyaṃ paramaṃ santiṃ, yogakkhemaṃ anuttaran’’ ti vatvā tameva paṭipattiṃ paribrūhayanto vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
