643594,128,1014,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ yaṃ yonupapajjāmi, devattaṃ atha mānusaṃ; "
643595,128,1015,2,9,1,44,6,"Bhoge me ūnatā natthi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643596,128,1016,2,10,1,38,6,"‘ ‘ Yāvatā caturo dīpā, sasamuddā sapabbatā; "
643597,128,1017,2,8,1,44,5,"Phalaṃ buddhassa datvāna, issaraṃ kārayāmahaṃ."
643598,128,1018,2,11,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Yāvatā ye pakkhigaṇā, ākāse uppatanti ce; "
643599,128,1019,2,8,1,43,5,"Tepi me vasamanventi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643600,128,1020,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Yāvatā vanasaṇḍamhi, yakkhā bhūtā ca rakkhasā; "
643601,128,1021,2,9,1,43,6,"Kumbhaṇḍā garuḷā cāpi, pāricariyaṃ upenti me."
643602,128,1022,2,12,1,41,8,"‘ ‘ Kummā soṇā madhukārā, ḍaṃsā ca makasā ubho; "
643603,128,1023,2,8,1,44,5,"Tepi maṃ vasamanventi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643604,128,1024,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Supaṇṇā nāma sakuṇā, pakkhijātā mahabbalā; "
643605,128,1025,2,9,1,45,6,"Tepi maṃ saraṇaṃ yanti, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643606,128,1026,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Yepi dīghāyukā nāgā, iddhimanto mahāyasā; "
643607,128,1027,2,8,1,44,5,"Tepi maṃ vasamanventi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643608,128,1028,2,12,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Sīhā byagghā ca dīpī ca, acchakokataracchakā; "
643609,128,1029,2,8,1,44,5,"Tepi maṃ vasamanventi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643610,128,1030,2,11,1,36,7,"‘ ‘ Osadhī tiṇavāsī ca, ye ca ākāsavāsino; "
643611,128,1031,2,9,1,46,6,"Sabbe maṃ saraṇaṃ yanti, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643612,128,1032,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Sududdasaṃ sunipuṇaṃ, gambhīraṃ suppakāsitaṃ; "
643613,128,1033,2,7,1,43,4,"Phassayitvā viharāmi, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643614,128,1034,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Vimokkhe aṭṭha phusitvā, viharāmi anāsavo; "
643615,128,1035,2,8,1,41,5,"Ātāpī nipako cāhaṃ, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643616,128,1036,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Ye phalaṭṭhā buddhaputtā, khīṇadosā mahāyasā; "
643617,128,1037,2,7,1,41,4,"Ahamaññataro tesaṃ, phaladānassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643618,128,1038,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Abhiññāpāramiṃ gantvā, sukkamūlena codito; "
643619,128,1039,2,7,1,36,4,"Sabbāsave pariññāya, viharāmi anāsavo."
643620,128,1040,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Tevijjā iddhipattā ca, buddhaputtā mahāyasā; "
643621,128,1041,2,8,1,40,5,"Dibbasotaṃ samāpannā, tesaṃ aññataro ahaṃ."
