643627,128,1047,2,4,1,24,2,3 . Sopākattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
643628,128,1048,2,8,1,54,6,Yathāpi ekaputtasmin ti āyasmato sopākattherassa gāthā. 
643629,128,1048,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
643630,128,1048,12,37,1,237,25,So kira purimabuddhesu katādhikāro hutvā tattha tattha vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ kusalaṃ upacinanto kakusandhassa bhagavato kāle aññatarassa kuṭumbikassa putto hutvā nibbatto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannacitto bījapūraphalāni satthu upanesi. 
643631,128,1048,38,43,1,37,4,Paṭiggahesi bhagavā anukampaṃ upādāya . 
643632,128,1048,44,56,1,125,12,So bhikkhusaṅghe ca abhippasanno salākabhattaṃ paṭṭhapetvā saṅghuddesavasena tiṇṇaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ yāvatāyukaṃ khīrabhattaṃ adāsi. 
643633,128,1048,57,71,1,140,14,So tehi puññakammehi aparāparaṃ devamanussesu sampattiṃ anubhavanto ekadā manussayoniyaṃ nibbatto ekassa paccekabuddhassa khīrabhattaṃ adāsi. 
643634,128,1048,72,89,1,166,17,Evaṃ tattha tattha puññāni katvā sugatīsu eva paribbhamanto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde purimakammanissandena sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarāya duggatitthiyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
643635,128,1048,90,107,1,137,17,Tassa mātā dasa māse kucchinā pariharitvā paripakke gabbhe vijāyanakāle vijāyituṃ asakkontī mucchaṃ āpajjitvā bahuvelaṃ matā viya nipajji. 
643636,128,1048,108,127,1,120,15,Taṃ ñātakā‘‘ matā’’ ti saññāya susānaṃ netvā citakaṃ āropetvā devatānubhāvena vātavuṭṭhiyā uṭṭhitāya aggiṃ adatvā pakkamiṃsu. 
643637,128,1048,128,135,1,69,6,Dārako pacchimabhāvikattā devatānubhāvena mātukucchito arogo nikkhami. 
643638,128,1048,136,139,1,20,3,Mātā pana kālamakāsi. 
643639,128,1048,140,151,1,102,11,Devatā taṃ gahetvā manussarūpena susānagopakassa gehe ṭhapetvā katipayakālaṃ patirūpena āhārena posesi. 
643640,128,1048,152,161,1,59,9,Tato paraṃ susānagopako ca naṃ attano puttaṃ katvā vaḍḍheti. 
643641,128,1048,162,173,1,80,11,So tathā vaḍḍhento tassa puttena supiyena nāma dārakena saddhiṃ kīḷanto vicarati. 
643642,128,1048,174,181,1,56,6,Tassa susāne jātasaṃvaḍḍhabhāvato {sopāko}ti samaññā ahosi. 
643643,128,1049,2,15,1,146,13,Athekadivasaṃ sattavassikaṃ taṃ bhagavā paccūsavelāya ñāṇajālaṃ pattharitvā veneyyabandhave oloketvā ñāṇajalantogadhaṃ disvā susānaṭṭhānaṃ agamāsi. 
643644,128,1049,16,24,1,84,8,Dārako pubbahetunā codiyamāno pasannamānaso satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā aṭṭhāsi. 
643645,128,1049,25,29,1,28,4,Satthā tassa dhammaṃ kathesi. 
643646,128,1049,30,47,1,90,13,So dhammaṃ sutvā pabbajjaṃ yācitvā‘‘ pitarā anuññātosī’’ ti vutto pitaraṃ satthu santikaṃ nesi. 
643647,128,1049,48,65,1,85,11,"Tassa pitā satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā‘‘ bhante, imaṃ dārakaṃ pabbājethā’’ ti anujāni. "
643648,128,1049,66,71,1,45,5,Satthā taṃ pabbājetvā mettābhāvanāya niyojesi. 
643649,128,1049,72,88,1,145,16,So mettākammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā susāne viharanto ca cirasseva mettājhānaṃ nibbattetvā jhānaṃ pādakaṃ katvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ sacchākāsi. 
643650,128,1049,89,102,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera2.45.1-7)–
643651,128,1050,2,10,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Kakusandho mahāvīro, sabbadhammāna pāragū; "
643652,128,1051,2,8,1,40,5,"Gaṇamhā vūpakaṭṭho so, agamāsi vanantaraṃ."
643653,128,1052,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Bījamiñjaṃ gahetvāna, latāya āvuṇiṃ ahaṃ; "
643654,128,1053,2,8,1,41,5,"Bhagavā tamhi samaye, jhāyate pabbatantare."
643655,128,1054,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Disvānahaṃ devadevaṃ, vippasannena cetasā; "
643656,128,1055,2,6,1,41,3,"Dakkhiṇeyyassa vīrassa, bījamiñjamadāsahaṃ."
643657,128,1056,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Imasmiṃyeva kappamhi, yaṃ miñjamadadiṃ tadā; "
643658,128,1057,2,7,1,43,4,"Duggatiṃ nābhijānāmi, bījamiñjassidaṃ phalaṃ."
643659,128,1058,2,16,1,51,9,‘ ‘ Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ… pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti. 
643660,128,1059,2,18,1,109,12,Arahā hutvā pana aññesaṃ sosānikabhikkhūnaṃ mettābhāvanāvidhiṃ dassento‘‘ yathāpi ekaputtasmin’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
643661,128,1060,2,10,1,32,4,33. Tattha {yathā}ti opammatthe nipāto. 
643662,128,1060,11,22,1,74,10,"Ekaputtasmin ti punāti ca kulavaṃsaṃ tāyati cāti putto, atrajādibhedo putto. "
643663,128,1060,23,29,1,38,5,"Eko putto ekaputto, tasmiṃ ekaputtasmiṃ. "
643664,128,1060,30,33,1,26,3,Visaye cetaṃ bhummavacanaṃ. 
643665,128,1060,34,43,1,90,9,Piyasmin ti piyāyitabbatāya ceva ekaputtatāya ca rūpasīlācārādīhi ca pemakaraṇaṭṭhānabhūte. 
643666,128,1060,44,61,1,111,13,"{Kusalī}ti kusalaṃ vuccati khemaṃ sotthibhāvo, taṃ labhitabbaṃ etassa atthīti kusalī, sattānaṃ hitesī mettajjhāsayo. "
643667,128,1060,62,67,1,32,4,Sabbesu {pāṇesū}ti sabbesu sattesu. 
643668,128,1060,68,79,1,68,9,"{Sabbatthā}ti sabbāsu disāsu sabbesu vā bhavādīsu, sabbāsu vā avatthāsu. "
643669,128,1060,80,127,1,350,39,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yathā ekaputtake piye manāpe mātāpitā kusalī ekantahitesī bhaveyya, evaṃ puratthimādibhedāsu sabbāsu disāsu, kāmabhavādibhedesu sabbesu bhavesu daharādibhedāsu sabbāsu avatthāsu ca ṭhitesu sabbesu sattesu ekantahitesitāya kusalī bhaveyya,‘‘ mitto udāsīno pañcatthiko’’ ti sīmaṃ akatvā sīmāsambhedavasena sabbattha ekarasaṃ mettaṃ bhāveyyāti. "
643670,128,1060,128,172,1,190,25,"Imaṃ pana gāthaṃ vatvā‘‘ sace tumhe āyasmanto evaṃ mettābhāvanaṃ anuyuñjeyyātha, ye te bhagavatā‘ sukhaṃ supatī’ tiādinā ( a. ni.11.15) ekādasa mettānisaṃsā vuttā, ekaṃsena tesaṃ bhāgino bhavathā’’ ti ovādamadāsi. "
643671,128,1061,2,4,1,33,2,Sopākattheragāthāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
643672,128,1062,2,4,1,24,2,4 . Posiyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
643673,128,1063,2,7,1,45,4,{Anāsannavarā}ti āyasmato posiyattherassa gāthā. 
643674,128,1063,8,10,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
643675,128,1063,11,34,1,191,23,So kira purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ bahuṃ kusalaṃ upacinitvā sugatīsu eva saṃsaranto ito dvenavute kappe tissassa bhagavato kāle migaluddo hutvā araññe vicarati. 
643676,128,1063,35,46,1,83,11,Atha bhagavā tassa anuggahaṃ kātuṃ araññaṃ gantvā tassa cakkhupathe attānaṃ dassesi. 
643677,128,1063,47,57,1,92,10,So bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannacitto āvudhaṃ nikkhipitvā upasaṅkamitvā añjaliṃ paggayha aṭṭhāsi. 
643678,128,1063,58,61,1,31,3,Bhagavā nisīditukāmataṃ dassesi. 
643679,128,1063,62,71,1,76,9,So tāvadeva tiṇamuṭṭhiyo gahetvā same bhūmibhāge sakkaccaṃ santharitvā adāsi. 
643680,128,1063,72,77,1,39,5,Nisīdi tattha bhagavā anukampaṃ upādāya. 
643681,128,1063,78,89,1,108,11,Nisinne pana bhagavati anappakaṃ pītisomanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedento bhagavantaṃ vanditvā sayampi ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
643682,128,1063,90,103,1,70,9,Atha bhagavā‘‘ ettakaṃ vaṭṭati imassa kusalabījan’’ ti uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi. 
643683,128,1063,104,110,1,49,6,Acirapakkante bhagavati taṃ sīho migarājā ghātesi. 
643684,128,1063,111,116,1,30,4,So kālaṅkato devaloke nibbatti.
643685,128,1063,117,137,1,150,16,‘‘ So kira bhagavati anupagacchante sīhena ghātito niraye nibbattissatī’’ ti taṃ disvā bhagavā sugatiyaṃ nibbattanatthaṃ kusalabījaropanatthañca upasaṅkami. 
643686,128,1064,2,22,1,202,20,So tattha yāvatāyukaṃ ṭhatvā tato devalokato cavitvā sugatīsuyeva parivattento imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarassa mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhino putto saṅgāmajitattherassa kaniṭṭhabhātā hutvā nibbatti. 
643687,128,1064,23,27,1,24,4,Posiyo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. 
643688,128,1064,28,54,1,267,25,So vayappatto dārapariggahaṃ katvā ekaṃ puttaṃ labhitvā antimabhavikatāya dhammatāya codiyamāno jātiādiṃ paṭicca uppannasaṃvego pabbajitvā araññaṃ pavisitvā vūpakaṭṭho hutvā catusaccakammaṭṭhānabhāvanaṃ anuyuñjanto nacirasseva vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
643689,128,1064,55,68,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera2.53.1-12)–
643690,128,1065,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Himavantassāvidūre, lambako nāma pabbato; "
643691,128,1066,2,8,1,45,5,"Tattheva tisso sambuddho, abbhokāsamhi caṅkami."
643692,128,1067,2,12,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Migaluddo tadā āsiṃ, araññe kānane ahaṃ; "
643693,128,1068,2,7,1,41,4,"Disvāna taṃ devadevaṃ, tiṇamuṭṭhimadāsahaṃ."
643694,128,1069,2,10,1,46,6,"‘ ‘ Nisīdanatthaṃ buddhassa, datvā cittaṃ pasādayiṃ; "
643695,128,1070,2,7,1,43,4,"Sambuddhaṃ abhivādetvā, pakkāmiṃ uttarāmukho."
643696,128,1071,2,9,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Aciraṃ gatamattassa, migarājā apothayi; "
643697,128,1072,2,9,1,42,6,"Sohena pothito, santo tattha kālaṅkato ahaṃ."
643698,128,1073,2,11,1,43,7,"‘ ‘ Āsanne me kataṃ kammaṃ, buddhaseṭṭhe anāsave; "
643699,128,1074,2,6,1,38,3,"Sumutto saravegova, devalokamagacchahaṃ."
643700,128,1075,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Yūpo tattha subho āsi, puññakammābhinimmito; "
643701,128,1076,2,7,1,42,4,"Sahassakaṇḍo satabheṇḍu, dhajālu haritāmayo."
643702,128,1077,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Pabhā niddhāvate tassa, sataraṃsīva uggato; "
643703,128,1078,2,7,1,37,4,"Ākiṇṇo devakaññāhi, āmodiṃ kāmakāmihaṃ."
643704,128,1079,2,9,1,37,5,"‘ ‘ Devalokā cavitvāna, sukkamūlena codito; "
643705,128,1080,2,7,1,43,4,"Āgantvāna manussattaṃ, pattomhi āsavakkhayaṃ."
643706,128,1081,2,8,1,37,4,"‘ ‘ Catunnavutito kappe, nisīdanamadāsahaṃ; "
643707,128,1082,2,8,1,43,5,"Duggatiṃ nābhijānāmi, tiṇamuṭṭhe idaṃ phalaṃ."
643708,128,1083,2,16,1,51,9,‘ ‘ Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ… pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti. 
643709,128,1084,2,13,1,92,11,Arahattaṃ pana patvā bhagavantaṃ vandituṃ sāvatthiṃ āgato ñātiṃ anukampāya ñātigehaṃ agamāsi. 
643710,128,1084,14,32,1,157,17,Tattha naṃ purāṇadutiyikā vanditvā āsanadānādinā paṭhamaṃ upāsikā viya vattaṃ dassetvā therassa ajjhāsayaṃ ajānantī pacchā itthikuttādīhi palobhetukāmā ahosi . 
643711,128,1084,33,51,1,103,14,Thero‘‘ aho andhabālā mādisepi nāma evaṃ paṭipajjatī’’ ti cintetvā kiñci avatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā araññameva gato. 
643712,128,1084,52,72,1,83,12,"Taṃ āraññakā bhikkhū‘‘ kiṃ, āvuso, atilahuṃ, nivattosi, ñātakehi na diṭṭhosī’’ ti pucchiṃsu. "
643713,128,1084,73,86,1,66,9,Thero tattha pavattiṃ ācikkhanto‘‘ anāsannavarā etā’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
643714,128,1085,2,37,1,181,26,"34. Tattha {anāsannavarā}ti etā itthiyo na āsannā anupagatā, dūre eva vā ṭhitā hutvā varā purisassa seṭṭhā hitāvahā, tañca kho niccameva sabbakālameva, na rattimeva, na divāpi, na rahovelāyapi. "
643715,128,1085,38,41,1,22,2,{Vijānatā}ti vijānantena.
643716,128,1085,42,52,1,33,5,"‘‘ Anāsannaparā’’ tipi pāḷi, so evattho. "
643717,128,1085,53,73,1,190,15,"Ayañhettha adhippāyo– caṇḍahatthiassamahiṃsasīhabyagghayakkharakkhasapisācāpi manussānaṃ anupasaṅkamanto varā seṭṭhā, na anatthāvahā, te pana upasaṅkamantā diṭṭhadhammikaṃyeva anatthaṃ kareyyuṃ. "
643718,128,1085,74,91,1,162,16,"Itthiyo pana upasaṅkamitvā diṭṭhadhammikaṃ samparāyikaṃ vimokkhanissitampi atthaṃ vināsetvā mahantaṃ anatthaṃ āpādenti, tasmā anāsannavarā etā niccameva vijānatāti. "
643719,128,1085,92,103,1,60,7,Idāni tamatthaṃ attūpanāyikaṃ katvā dassento‘‘ gāmā’’ tiādimāha. 
643720,128,1085,104,108,1,19,3,Tattha {gāmā}ti gāmaṃ. 
643721,128,1085,109,113,1,35,4,Upayogatthe hi etaṃ nissakkavacanaṃ. 
643722,128,1085,114,118,1,32,3,{Araññamāgammā}ti araññato āgantvā. 
