644089,128,1233,2,4,1,22,2,4 . Sānuttheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
644090,128,1234,2,11,1,52,7,Mataṃ vā amma {rodantī}ti āyasmato sānuttherassa gāthā. 
644091,128,1234,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
644092,128,1234,15,33,1,191,18,Sopi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto ito catunavute kappe siddhatthassa bhagavato hatthapādadhovanamukhavikkhālanānaṃ atthāya udakaṃ upanesi. 
644093,128,1234,34,40,1,50,6,Satthā hi bhojanakāle hatthapāde dhovitukāmo ahosi. 
644094,128,1234,41,47,1,44,6,So satthu ākāraṃ sallakkhetvā udakaṃ upanesi. 
644095,128,1234,48,55,1,65,7,Bhagavā hatthapāde dhovitvā bhuñjitvā mukhaṃ vikkhāletukāmo ahosi. 
644096,128,1234,56,62,1,33,5,So tampi ñatvā mukhodakaṃ upanesi. 
644097,128,1234,63,68,1,55,5,Satthā mukhaṃ vikkhāletvā mukhadhovanakiccaṃ niṭṭhāpesi. 
644098,128,1234,69,77,1,66,8,Evaṃ bhagavā anukampaṃ upādāya tena karīyamānaṃ veyyāvaccaṃ sādiyi. 
644099,128,1234,78,96,1,169,18,So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarassa upāsakassa gehe paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
644100,128,1234,97,111,1,103,13,"Tasmiṃ gabbhagateyeva pitā pavāsaṃ gato, upāsikā dasamāsaccayena puttaṃ vijāyitvā sānū tissa nāmaṃ akāsi. "
644101,128,1234,112,131,1,140,14,"Tasmiṃ anukkamena vaḍḍhante sattavassikaṃyeva naṃ bhikkhūnaṃ santike pabbājesi,‘‘ evamayaṃ anantarāyo vaḍḍhitvā accantasukhabhāgī bhavissatī’’ ti."
644102,128,1234,132,156,1,175,19,‘‘ So sānusāmaṇero’’ ti paññāto paññavā vattasampanno bahussuto dhammakathiko sattesu mettajjhāsayo hutvā devamanussānaṃ piyo ahosi manāpoti sabbaṃ sānusutte āgatanayena veditabbaṃ. 
644103,128,1235,2,7,1,46,5,Tassa atītajātiyaṃ mātā yakkhayoniyaṃ nibbatti. 
644104,128,1235,8,21,1,71,9,Taṃ yakkhā‘‘ sānuttherassa ayaṃ mātā’’ ti garucittikārabahulā hutvā mānenti. 
644105,128,1235,22,37,1,159,15,Evaṃ gacchante kāle puthujjanabhāvassa ādīnavaṃ vibhāventaṃ viya ekadivasaṃ sānussa yoniso manasikārābhāvā ayoniso ummujjantassa vibbhamitukāmatācittaṃ uppajji. 
644106,128,1235,38,44,1,50,6,Taṃ tassa yakkhinimātā ñatvā manussamātuyā ārocesi–
644107,128,1235,45,61,1,59,9,"‘‘ tava putto, sānu,‘ vibbhamissāmī’ ti cittaṃ uppādesi, tasmā tvaṃ–"
644108,128,1236,2,11,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Sānuṃ pabuddhaṃ vajjāsi, yakkhānaṃ vacanaṃ idaṃ; "
644109,128,1237,2,11,1,41,8,"Mākāsi pāpakaṃ kammaṃ, āvi vā yadi vā raho."
644110,128,1238,2,13,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Sace tvaṃ pāpakaṃ kammaṃ, karissasi karosi vā; "
644111,128,1239,2,33,1,46,7,"Na te dukkhā pamutyatthi, uppaccāpi palāyato’’ ti.( saṃ. ni.1.239; dha. pa. aṭṭha.2.325 sānusāmaṇeravatthu)– "
644112,128,1240,2,7,1,15,3,Evaṃ bhaṇāhī’’ ti. 
644113,128,1240,8,13,1,49,5,Evañca pana vatvā yakkhinimātā tatthevantaradhāyi. 
644114,128,1240,14,21,1,74,7,Manussamātā pana taṃ sutvā paridevasokasamāpannā cetodukkhasamappitā ahosi. 
644115,128,1240,22,74,1,231,35,"Atha sānusāmaṇero pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya mātu santikaṃ upagato mātaraṃ rodamānaṃ disvā‘‘ amma, kiṃ nissāya rodasī’’ ti vatvā‘‘ taṃ nissāyā’’ ti ca vutto mātu‘‘ mataṃ vā, amma, rodanti, yo vā jīvaṃ na dissatī’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. "
644116,128,1241,2,6,1,9,1,44. Tassattho–
644117,128,1241,7,57,1,282,43,"‘‘ amma, rodantā nāma ñātakā mittā vā attano ñātakaṃ mittaṃ vā mataṃ uddissa rodanti paralokaṃ gatattā, yo vā ñātako mitto vā jīvaṃ jīvanto desantaraṃ pakkantatāya ca na dissati, taṃ vā uddissa rodanti, ubhayampetaṃ mayi na vijjati, evaṃ sante jīvantaṃ dharamānaṃ maṃ purato ṭhitaṃ passantī; "
644118,128,1241,58,63,1,17,3,"kasmā, amma, rodasi? "
