644167,128,1271,2,6,1,40,3,"Sattaratanasampanno , cakkavattī mahabbalo."
644168,128,1272,2,16,1,51,9,‘ ‘ Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ… pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti. 
