644822,128,1612,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
644823,128,1612,14,34,1,175,20,Sopi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni karonto ito ekanavute kappe yakkhasenāpati hutvā vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso dibbavatthena pūjaṃ akāsi. 
644824,128,1612,35,55,1,144,15,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sakkesu devadahanigame sākiyarājakule nibbatti,‘‘ sammodakumāro’’ tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
644825,128,1612,56,62,1,45,6,Athassa daharakāle vātarogena pādā na vahiṃsu. 
644826,128,1612,63,69,1,41,6,So katipayaṃ kālaṃ pīṭhasappī viya vicari. 
644827,128,1612,70,75,1,29,4,Tenassa {pakkho}ti samaññā jātā. 
644828,128,1612,76,94,1,165,17,"Pacchā arogakālepi tatheva naṃ sañjānanti, so bhagavato ñātisamāgame pāṭihāriyaṃ disvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā katapubbakicco kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā araññe viharati. "
644829,128,1612,95,104,1,90,9,Athekadivasaṃ gāmaṃ piṇḍāya pavisituṃ gacchanto antarāmagge aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi. 
644830,128,1612,105,119,1,100,13,"Tasmiñca samaye aññataro kulalo maṃsapesiṃ ādāya ākāsena gacchati, taṃ bahū kulalā anupatitvā pātesuṃ. "
644831,128,1612,120,125,1,38,5,Pātitaṃ maṃsapesiṃ eko kulalo aggahesi. 
644832,128,1612,126,174,1,314,36,"Taṃ añño acchinditvā gaṇhi, taṃ disvā thero‘‘ yathāyaṃ maṃsapesi, evaṃ kāmā nāma bahusādhāraṇā bahudukkhā bahupāyāsā’’ ti– kāmesu ādīnavaṃ nekkhamme ca ānisaṃsaṃ paccavekkhitvā vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā‘‘ aniccan’’ tiādinā manasikaronto piṇḍāya caritvā katabhattakicco divāṭṭhāne nisīditvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
