644868,128,1636,8,10,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
644869,128,1636,11,45,1,310,33,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto ito ekanavute kappe vipassissa bhagavato kāle vibhavasampanne kule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ vipassiṃ bhagavantaṃ mahatiyā parisāya parivutaṃ dhammaṃ desentaṃ disvā pasannamānaso catūhi suvaṇṇapupphehi pūjesi. 
644870,128,1636,46,59,1,127,12,"Bhagavā tassa pasādasaṃvaḍḍhanatthaṃ tathārūpaṃ iddhābhisaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkhāresi, yathā suvaṇṇābhā sakalaṃ taṃ padesaṃ ottharati. "
644871,128,1636,60,98,1,319,36,Taṃ disvā bhiyyosomattāya pasannamānaso hutvā bhagavantaṃ vanditvā taṃ nimittaṃ gahetvā attano gehaṃ gantvā buddhārammaṇaṃ pītiṃ avijahanto kenaci rogena kālaṃ katvā tusitesu upapanno aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājānaṃ bimbisāraṃ paṭicca ambapāliyā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ gaṇhi. 
644872,128,1636,99,115,1,160,16,Rājā hi bimbisāro taruṇakāle ambapāliyā rūpasampattiṃ sutvā sañjātābhilāso katipayamanussaparivāro aññātakavesena vesāliṃ gantvā ekarattiṃ tāya saṃvāsaṃ kappesi. 
644873,128,1636,116,122,1,46,6,Tadā ayaṃ tassā kucchimhi paṭisandhiṃ aggahesi. 
644874,128,1636,123,129,1,46,6,Sā ca gabbhassa patiṭṭhitabhāvaṃ tassa ārocesi. 
644875,128,1636,130,136,1,54,6,Rājāpi attānaṃ jānāpetvā dātabbayuttakaṃ datvā pakkāmi. 
644876,128,1636,137,156,1,103,12,"Sā gabbhassa paripākamanvāya puttaṃ vijāyi,‘‘ vimalo’’ tissa nāmaṃ ahosi, pacchā {vimalakoṇḍañño}ti paññāyittha. "
644877,128,1636,157,171,1,149,14,So vayappatto bhagavato vesāligamane buddhānubhāvaṃ disvā pasannamānaso pabbajitvā katapubbakicco vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
