644971,128,1693,2,4,1,25,2,6 . Meghiyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
644972,128,1694,2,9,1,50,5,Anusāsi {mahāvīro}ti āyasmato meghiyattherassa gāthā. 
644973,128,1694,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
644974,128,1694,13,31,1,157,18,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave kusalabījāni ropento ito ekanavute kappe vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ pāpuṇi. 
644975,128,1694,32,40,1,85,8,Tasmiñca samaye vipassī bhagavā buddhakiccassa pariyosānamāgamma āyusaṅkhāraṃ ossajji. 
644976,128,1694,41,47,1,58,6,Tena pathavīkampādīsu uppannesu mahājano bhītatasito ahosi. 
644977,128,1694,48,55,1,60,7,Atha naṃ vessavaṇo mahārājā tamatthaṃ vibhāvetvā samassāsesi. 
644978,128,1694,56,61,1,38,5,Taṃ sutvā mahājano saṃvegappatto ahosi. 
644979,128,1694,62,71,1,107,9,Tatthāyaṃ kulaputto buddhānubhāvaṃ sutvā satthari sañjātagāravabahumāno uḷāraṃ pītisomanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedesi. 
644980,128,1694,72,88,1,134,14,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthusmiṃ sākiyarājakule nibbatti, tassa {meghiyo}ti nāmaṃ ahosi. "
644981,128,1694,89,126,1,327,35,So vayappatto satthu santike pabbajitvā bhagavantaṃ upaṭṭhahanto bhagavati jālikāyaṃ viharante kimikālāya nadiyā tīre ramaṇīyaṃ ambavanaṃ disvā tattha viharitukāmo dve vāre bhagavatā vāretvā tatiyavāraṃ vissajjito tattha gantvā micchāvitakkamakkhikāhi khajjamāno cittasamādhiṃ alabhitvā satthu santikaṃ gantvā tamatthaṃ ārocesi. 
644982,128,1694,127,150,1,108,12,"Athassa bhagavā‘‘ aparipakkāya, meghiya, cetovimuttiyā pañca dhammā paripākāya saṃvattantī’’ tiādinā( udā.31) ovādaṃ adāsi. "
644983,128,1694,151,159,1,60,8,So tasmiṃ ovāde ṭhatvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
644984,128,1694,160,173,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.12.57-65)–
