645007,128,1716,13,16,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
645008,128,1717,2,22,1,119,13,"Tattha {anusāsī}ti‘‘ aparipakkāya, meghiya, cetovimuttiyā pañca dhammā paripākāya saṃvattantī’’ tiādinā ovadi anusiṭṭhiṃ adāsi. "
645009,128,1717,23,33,1,155,8,"{Mahāvīro}ti mahāvikkanto, vīriyapāramipāripūriyā caturaṅgasamannāgatavīriyādhiṭṭhānena anaññasādhāraṇacatubbidhasammappadhānasampattiyā ca mahāvīriyoti attho. "
645010,128,1717,34,49,1,132,13,"Sabbadhammāna {pāragū}ti sabbesañca ñeyyadhammānaṃ pāraṃ pariyantaṃ ñāṇagamanena gato adhigatoti sabbadhammāna pāragū, sabbaññūti attho. "
645011,128,1717,50,60,1,101,10,Sabbesaṃ vā saṅkhatadhammānaṃ pārabhūtaṃ nibbānaṃ sayambhūñāṇena gato adhigatoti sabbadhammāna pāragū. 
645012,128,1717,61,72,1,95,10,Tassāhaṃ dhammaṃ {sutvānā}ti tassa buddhassa bhagavato sāmukkaṃsikaṃ taṃ catusaccadhammaṃ suṇitvā. 
645013,128,1717,73,85,1,99,11,Vihāsiṃ {santike}ti ambavane micchāvitakkehi upadduto cālikā vihāraṃ gantvā satthu samīpeyeva vihāsiṃ. 
645014,128,1717,86,93,1,57,5,"{Sato}ti satimā, samathavipassanābhāvanāya appamattoti attho. "
645015,128,1717,94,132,1,119,20,"Ahan ti idaṃ yathā‘‘ anusāsī’’ ti ettha‘‘ man’’ ti evaṃ‘‘ vijjā anuppattā, kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti ettha‘‘ mayā’’ ti pariṇāmetabbaṃ."
645016,128,1717,133,149,1,132,12,‘‘ Kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti ca iminā yathāvuttaṃ vijjāttayānuppattimeva satthu ovādapaṭikaraṇabhāvadassanena pariyāyantarena pakāseti. 
