645019,128,1719,2,4,1,35,2,7 . Ekadhammasavanīyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
645020,128,1720,2,10,1,66,7,Kilesā jhāpitā mayhan ti āyasmato ekadhammasavanīyattherassa gāthā. 
645021,128,1720,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645022,128,1720,14,38,1,211,23,So kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle rukkhadevatā hutvā nibbatto katipaye bhikkhū maggamūḷhe mahāraññe vicarante disvā anukampamāno attano bhavanato otaritvā te samassāsetvā bhojetvā yathādhippetaṭṭhānaṃ pāpesi. 
645023,128,1720,39,56,1,148,17,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto kassape bhagavati loke uppajjitvā katabuddhakicce parinibbute tasmiṃ kāle bārāṇasirājā kikī nāma ahosi. 
645024,128,1720,57,64,1,52,7,Tasmiṃ kālaṅkate tassa puthuvindarājā nāma putto āsi. 
645025,128,1720,65,69,1,23,4,Tassa putto susāmo nāma. 
645026,128,1720,70,110,1,258,30,"Tassa putto kikībrahmadatto nāma hutvā rajjaṃ kārento sāsane antarahite dhammassavanaṃ alabhanto,‘‘ yo dhammaṃ deseti, tassa sahassaṃ dammī’’ ti ghosāpetvā ekampi dhammakathikaṃ alabhanto,‘‘ mayhaṃ pitupitāmahādīnaṃ kāle dhammo saṃvattati, dhammakathikā sulabhā ahesuṃ. "
645027,128,1720,111,116,1,53,5,Idāni pana catuppadikagāthāmattampi kathento dullabho. 
645028,128,1720,117,148,1,180,23,"Yāva dhammasaññā na vinassati, tāvadeva pabbajissāmī’’ ti rajjaṃ pahāya himavantaṃ uddissa gacchantaṃ sakko devarājā āgantvā,‘‘ aniccā vata saṅkhārā’’ ti gāthāya dhammaṃ kathetvā nivattesi. "
645029,128,1720,149,172,1,221,22,So nivattitvā bahuṃ puññaṃ katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde setabyanagare seṭṭhikule nibbattitvā vayappatto bhagavati setabyanagare siṃsapāvane viharante satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
645030,128,1720,173,190,1,85,12,"Tassa satthā ajjhāsayaṃ oloketvā,‘‘ aniccā vata saṅkhārā’’ ti imāya gāthāya dhammaṃ desesi. "
645031,128,1720,191,210,1,216,19,Tassa tattha katādhikāratāya so aniccasaññāya pākaṭataraṃ hutvā upaṭṭhitāya paṭiladdhasaṃvego pabbajitvā dhammasammasanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā dukkhasaññaṃ anattasaññañca manasikaronto vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
