645065,128,1741,2,4,1,27,2,8 . Ekudāniyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
645066,128,1742,2,9,1,58,5,Adhicetaso {appamajjato}ti āyasmato ekudāniyattherassa gāthā. 
645067,128,1742,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645068,128,1742,13,51,1,287,31,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto atthadassissa bhagavato kāle yakkhasenāpati hutvā nibbatto satthari parinibbute,‘‘ alābhā vata me, dulladdhaṃ vata me, yohaṃ satthudharamānakāle dānādipuññaṃ kātuṃ nālatthan’’ ti paridevasokamāpanno ahosi. "
645069,128,1742,52,63,1,79,11,Atha naṃ sāgaro nāma satthu sāvako sokaṃ vinodetvā satthu thūpapūjāyaṃ niyojesi. 
645070,128,1742,64,89,1,185,24,So pañca vassāni thūpaṃ pūjetvā tato cuto tena puññena devamanussesu eva saṃsaranto kassapassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto kālena kālaṃ satthu santikaṃ upasaṅkami. 
645071,128,1742,90,103,1,66,9,Tasmiñca samaye satthā‘‘ adhicetaso’’ ti gāthāya sāvake abhiṇhaṃ ovadi. 
645072,128,1742,104,109,1,31,5,So taṃ sutvā saddhājāto pabbaji. 
645073,128,1742,110,117,1,55,7,Pabbajitvā ca pana tameva gāthaṃ punappunaṃ parivatteti. 
645074,128,1742,118,128,1,102,10,So tattha vīsativassasahassāni samaṇadhammaṃ karonto ñāṇassa aparipakkattā visesaṃ nibbattetu nāsakkhi. 
645075,128,1742,129,158,1,300,29,Tato pana cuto devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ vibhavasampannassa brāhmaṇassa putto hutvā nibbatto viññutaṃ patvā jetavanapaṭiggahaṇasamaye buddhānubhāvaṃ disvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā katapubbakicco araññe viharanto satthu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
645076,128,1742,159,178,1,119,14,Tasmiñca samaye satthā āyasmantaṃ sāriputtaṃ attano avidūre adhicittamanuyuttaṃ disvā‘‘ adhicetaso’’ ti imaṃ udānaṃ udānesi. 
645077,128,1742,179,197,1,124,16,"Taṃ sutvā ayaṃ cirakālaṃ bhāvanāya araññe viharantopi kālena kālaṃ tameva gāthaṃ udāneti, tenassa {ekudāniyo}ti samaññā udapādi. "
645078,128,1742,198,206,1,77,8,So athekadivasaṃ cittekaggataṃ labhitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
