645103,128,1766,2,5,1,21,3,Imameva gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
645104,128,1767,2,13,1,100,8,"Tattha {adhicetaso}ti adhicittavato, sabbacittānaṃ adhikena arahattaphalacittena samannāgatassāti attho. "
645105,128,1767,14,24,1,99,8,"{Appamajjato}ti nappamajjato, appamādena anavajjadhammesu sātaccakiriyāya samannāgatassāti vuttaṃ hoti. "
645106,128,1767,25,75,1,191,25,"{Munino}ti‘‘ yo munāti ubho loke, muni tena pavuccatī’’ ti( dha. pa.269; mahāni.149; cūḷani. mettagūmāṇavapucchāniddesa21) evaṃ ubhayalokamunanena vā, monaṃ vuccati ñāṇaṃ, tena arahattaphalapaññāsaṅkhātena monena samannāgatatāya vā khīṇāsavo muni nāma, tassa munino. "
645107,128,1767,76,89,1,133,11,"Monapathesu {sikkhato}ti arahattañāṇasaṅkhātassa monassa pathesu upāyamaggesu sattatiṃsabodhipakkhiyadhammesu, tīsu vā sikkhāsu sikkhato. "
645108,128,1767,90,94,1,41,4,Idañca pubbabhāgapaṭipadaṃ gahetvā vuttaṃ. 
645109,128,1767,95,111,1,117,14,"Pariniṭṭhitasikkho hi arahā, tasmā evaṃ sikkhato, imāya sikkhāya munibhāvaṃ pattassa muninoti evamettha attho daṭṭhabbo. "
645110,128,1767,112,130,1,196,15,"Yasmā cetadevaṃ tasmā heṭṭhimamaggaphalacittānaṃ vasena adhicetaso, catusaccasambodhipaṭipattiyaṃ appamādavasena appamajjato, aggamaggañāṇasamannāgamena muninoti evametesaṃ padānaṃ attho yujjatiyeva. "
645111,128,1767,131,142,1,60,7,Atha vā‘‘ appamajjato sikkhato’’ padhānahetū akkhātāti daṭṭhabbā. 
