645120,128,1771,2,4,1,24,2,9 . Channattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
645121,128,1772,2,11,1,66,8,Sutvāna dhammaṃ mahato mahārasan ti āyasmato channattherassa gāthā. 
645122,128,1772,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645123,128,1772,15,43,1,292,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ siddhatthaṃ bhagavantaṃ aññataraṃ rukkhamūlaṃ upagacchantaṃ disvā pasannacitto mudusamphassaṃ paṇṇasantharaṃ santharitvā adāsi. 
645124,128,1772,44,51,1,42,6,Pupphehi ca samantato okiritvā pūjaṃ akāsi. 
645125,128,1772,52,79,1,220,25,"So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā punapi aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto amhākaṃ bhagavato kāle suddhodanamahārājassa gehe dāsiyā kucchimhi nibbatti, channo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi, bodhisattena sahajāto. "
645126,128,1772,80,120,1,321,34,"So satthu ñātisamāgame paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā bhagavati pemena,‘‘ amhākaṃ buddho, amhākaṃ dhammo’’ ti mamattaṃ uppādetvā sinehaṃ chindituṃ asakkonto samaṇadhammaṃ akatvā satthari parinibbute satthārā āṇattavidhinā katena brahmadaṇḍena santajjito saṃvegappatto hutvā sinehaṃ chinditvā vipassanto nacireneva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
