645289,128,1861,13,16,1,13,2,{Susū}ti taruṇo. 
645290,128,1861,17,20,1,29,2,{Vaḍḍhitaggo}ti pavaḍḍhitasākho. 
645291,128,1861,21,27,1,59,5,{Susuvaḍḍhitaggo}ti vā suṭṭhu vaḍḍhitasākho sañjātapattasākho. 
645292,128,1861,28,34,1,59,5,{Dunnikkhamo}ti veḷugumbato nikkhāmetuṃ nīharituṃ asakkuṇeyyo. 
645293,128,1861,35,43,1,64,6,"{Pasākhajāto}ti jātapasākho, sākhānampi pabbe pabbe uppannaanusākho. "
645294,128,1861,44,69,1,235,23,"Evaṃ ahaṃ {bhariyāyānītāyā}ti yathā vaṃso vaḍḍhitaggo vaṃsantaresu saṃsaṭṭha sākhāpasākho veḷugumbato dunnīharaṇīyo hoti, evaṃ ahampi bhariyāya mayhaṃ ānītāya puttadhītādivasena vaḍḍhitaggo āsattivasena gharāvāsato dunnīharaṇīyo bhaveyyaṃ. "
645295,128,1861,70,93,1,199,21,"Yathā pana vaṃsakaḷīro asañjātasākhabandho veḷugumbato sunīharaṇīyova hoti, evaṃ ahampi asañjātaputtadārādibandho sunīharaṇīyo homi, tasmā anānītāya eva bhariyāya anumañña maṃ attanāva maṃ anujānāpetvā. "
645296,128,1861,94,127,1,150,21,"Pabbajitomhi {dānī}ti,‘‘ idāni pana pabbajito amhi, sādhu suṭṭhū’’ ti attano nekkhammābhiratiṃ pakāsesi, atha vā‘‘ anumañña maṃ pabbajitomhi dānī’’ ti mātu katheti. "
645297,128,1861,128,152,1,147,19,"Ayañhettha attho– yadipi tāya pubbe nānumataṃ, idāni pana pabbajito amhi, tasmā anumañña anujānāhi maṃ samaṇabhāveyeva ṭhātuṃ, nāhaṃ tayā nivattanīyoti . "
645298,128,1861,153,164,1,102,11,Evaṃ pana kathento yathāṭhitova vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā maggapaṭipāṭiyā kilese khepetvā chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
