645662,128,2093,2,11,1,61,8,Yaṃ mayā pakataṃ pāpan ti āyasmato samitiguttattherassa gāthā. 
645663,128,2093,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645664,128,2093,15,36,1,197,21,Sopi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto bhagavantaṃ passitvā pasannacitto jātisumanapupphehi pūjaṃ akāsi. 
645665,128,2093,37,52,1,121,14,"So tena puññakammena yattha yattha bhave nibbatti, tattha tattha kularūpaparivārasampadāya aññe satte abhibhavitvā aṭṭhāsi. "
645666,128,2093,53,76,1,151,18,"Ekasmiṃ pana attabhāve aññataraṃ paccekabuddhaṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ disvā‘‘ ayaṃ muṇḍako kuṭṭhī maññe, tenāyaṃ paṭicchādetvā vicaratī’’ ti niṭṭhubhitvā pakkāmi. "
645667,128,2093,77,114,1,260,30,"So tena kammena bahuṃ kālaṃ niraye paccitvā kassapassa bhagavato kāle manussaloke nibbatto paribbājakapabbajjaṃ upagato ekaṃ sīlācārasampannaṃ upāsakaṃ disvā dosantaro hutvā,‘‘ kuṭṭharogī bhaveyyāsī’’ ti akkosi, nhānatitthe ca manussehi ṭhapitāni nhānacuṇṇāni dūsesi. "
645668,128,2093,115,138,1,181,22,"So tena kammena puna niraye nibbattitvā bahūni vassāni dukkhaṃ anubhavitvā imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarassa brāhmaṇassa putto hutvā nibbatti, samitigutto tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
645669,128,2093,139,149,1,98,10,So vayappatto satthu dhammadesanaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā suvisuddhasīlo hutvā viharati. 
645670,128,2093,150,162,1,112,11,"Tassa purimakammanissandena kuṭṭharogo uppajji, tena tassa sarīrāvayavā yebhuyyena chinnabhinnā hutvā paggharanti. "
645671,128,2093,163,166,1,23,3,So gilānasālāyaṃ vasati. 
645672,128,2093,167,190,1,166,19,"Athekadivasaṃ dhammasenāpati gilānapucchaṃ gantvā tattha tattha gilāne bhikkhū pucchanto taṃ bhikkhuṃ disvā‘‘ āvuso, yāvatā khandhappavatti nāma, sabbaṃ dukkhameva vedanā. "
645673,128,2093,191,203,1,90,9,Khandhesu pana asantesuyeva natthi dukkhan’’ ti vedanānupassanākammaṭṭhānaṃ kathetvā agamāsi. 
645674,128,2093,204,212,1,68,8,So therassa ovāde ṭhatvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā chaḷabhiññā sacchākāsi. 
