645708,128,2118,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645709,128,2118,13,36,1,191,22,"Ayaṃ kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā tīsu vedesu aññesu ca brāhmaṇasippesu nipphattiṃ gato, so ekadivasaṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sumanapupphehi pūjaṃ akāsi. "
645710,128,2118,37,45,1,57,8,Karonto ca satthu samantato upari ca pupphamuṭṭhiyo khipi. 
645711,128,2118,46,51,1,59,5,Buddhānubhāvena pupphāni pupphāsanākārena sattāhaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu. 
645712,128,2118,52,59,1,59,7,So taṃ acchariyaṃ disvā bhiyyosomattāya pasannamānaso ahosi. 
645713,128,2118,60,79,1,177,18,"Aparāparaṃ puññāni karonto kappasatasahassaṃ sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ aññatarassa udiccabrāhmaṇassa putto hutvā nibbatti, kassapo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
645714,128,2118,80,84,1,36,4,Tassa daharakāleyeva pitā kālamakāsi. 
645715,128,2118,85,88,1,20,3,Mātā taṃ paṭijaggati. 
645716,128,2118,89,119,1,276,30,So ekadivasaṃ jetavanaṃ gato bhagavato dhammadesanaṃ sutvā hetusampannatāya tasmiṃyeva āsane sotāpanno hutvā mātu santikaṃ gantvā anujānāpetvā pabbajito satthari vuṭṭhavasse pavāretvā janapadacārikaṃ pakkante sayampi satthārā saddhiṃ gantukāmo āpucchituṃ mātu santikaṃ agamāsi. 
