645753,128,2143,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645754,128,2143,12,40,1,289,28,So kira purimabuddhesu katādhikāro ito aṭṭhārasakappasatamatthake atthadassissa bhagavato kāle candabhāgāya nadiyā tīre kinnarayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā pupphabhakkho pupphanivasano hutvā viharanto ākāsena gacchantaṃ atthadassiṃ bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannacitto pūjetukāmo añjaliṃ paggayha aṭṭhāsi. 
645755,128,2143,41,52,1,87,10,Bhagavā tassa ajjhāsayaṃ ñatvā ākāsato oruyha aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle pallaṅkena nisīdi. 
645756,128,2143,53,65,1,105,12,Kinnaro candanasāraṃ ghaṃsitvā candanagandhena pupphehi ca pūjaṃ katvā vanditvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
645757,128,2143,66,82,1,113,13,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde mallarājakule nibbatti, tassa {sīho}ti nāmaṃ ahosi. "
645758,128,2143,83,90,1,60,7,So bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
645759,128,2143,91,97,1,48,6,Satthā tassa ajjhāsayaṃ oloketvā dhammaṃ kathesi. 
645760,128,2143,98,107,1,81,9,So dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā araññe viharati. 
645761,128,2143,108,121,1,83,11,"Tassa cittaṃ nānārammaṇe vidhāvati, ekaggaṃ na hoti, sakatthaṃ nipphādetuṃ na sakkoti. "
