645873,128,2214,2,10,1,63,7,Ito bahiddhā puthuaññavādinan ti āyasmato nāgitattherassa gāthā. 
645874,128,2214,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
645875,128,2214,14,35,1,187,21,Ayaṃ kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle nārado nāma brāhmaṇo hutvā ekadivasaṃ māḷake nisinno bhagavantaṃ bhikkhusaṅghena purakkhataṃ gacchantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso tīhi gāthāhi abhitthavi. 
645876,128,2214,36,56,1,178,19,"So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthunagare sakyarājakule nibbatti, nāgito tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
645877,128,2214,57,80,1,130,12,So bhagavati kapilavatthusmiṃ viharante madhupiṇḍikasuttaṃ( ma. ni.1.199 ādayo) sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
