646088,128,2332,2,4,1,24,2,2 . Vijayattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
646089,128,2333,2,9,1,53,5,Yassāsavā {parikkhīṇā}ti āyasmato vijayattherassa gāthā. 
646090,128,2333,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646091,128,2333,13,36,1,209,22,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro piyadassissa bhagavato kāle vibhavasampanne kule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto satthari parinibbute tassa thūpassa ratanakhacitaṃ vedikaṃ kāretvā tattha uḷāraṃ vedikāmahaṃ kāresi. 
646092,128,2333,37,44,1,60,7,So tena puññakammena anekasate attabhāve maṇiobhāsena vicari. 
646093,128,2333,45,58,1,108,12,"Evaṃ devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, vijayo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
646094,128,2333,59,80,1,212,21,So vayappatto brāhmaṇavijjāsu nipphattiṃ gato tāpasapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā araññāyatane jhānalābhī hutvā viharanto buddhuppādaṃ sutvā uppannappasādo satthu santikaṃ upasaṅkamitvā satthāraṃ vanditvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
646095,128,2333,81,85,1,27,4,Tassa satthā dhammaṃ desesi. 
646096,128,2333,86,95,1,79,9,So dhammaṃ sutvā pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
