646117,128,2347,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646118,128,2347,13,50,1,297,33,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannamānaso satthu kiñci dātabbayuttakaṃ alabhanto‘‘ handāhaṃ kāyasāraṃ puññaṃ karissāmī’’ ti satthu gamanamaggaṃ sodhetvā samaṃ akāsi. 
646119,128,2347,51,57,1,39,5,Satthā tena tathākataṃ maggaṃ paṭipajji . 
646120,128,2347,58,73,1,150,15,So tattha bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso vanditvā añjaliṃ paggayha pasannacitto yāva dassanupacārasamatikkamā buddhārammaṇaṃ pītiṃ avijahanto aṭṭhāsi. 
646121,128,2347,74,104,1,271,29,"So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbatto aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ sambhāvanīyassa kuṭumbiyassa putto hutvā nibbatti, erako tissa nāmaṃ ahosi abhirūpo dassanīyo pāsādiko itikattabbatāsu paramena veyyattiyena samannāgato. "
646122,128,2347,105,119,1,106,13,Tassa mātāpitaro kulena rūpena ācārena vayena kosallena ca anucchavikaṃ dārikaṃ ānetvā vivāhakammaṃ akaṃsu . 
646123,128,2347,120,143,1,201,22,"So tāya saddhiṃ saṃvāsena gehe vasanto pacchimabhavikattā kenacideva saṃvegavatthunā saṃsāre saṃviggamānaso satthu santikaṃ gantvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbaji, tassa satthā kammaṭṭhānaṃ adāsi. "
646124,128,2347,144,150,1,71,6,So kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā katipayadivasātikkamena ukkaṇṭhābhibhūto vihāsi. 
646125,128,2347,151,167,1,85,12,Atha satthā tassa cittappavattiṃ ñatvā ovādavasena‘‘ dukkhā kāmā erakā’’ ti gāthaṃ abhāsi. 
646126,128,2347,168,196,1,198,23,"So taṃ sutvā‘‘ ayuttaṃ mayā kataṃ, yohaṃ evarūpassa satthu santike kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā taṃ vissajjento micchāvitakkabahulo vihāsin’’ ti saṃvegajāto vipassanāya yuttappayutto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
