646156,128,2365,2,4,1,25,2,4 . Mettajittheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
646157,128,2366,2,12,1,57,7,Namo hi tassa {bhagavato}ti āyasmato mettajittherassa gāthā. 
646158,128,2366,13,15,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646159,128,2366,16,34,1,162,18,So kira anomadassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto sāsane abhippasanno hutvā bodhirukkhassa iṭṭhakāhi vedikaṃ cinitvā sudhāparikammaṃ kāresi. 
