646268,128,2418,15,21,1,67,5,{Cajitvānā}ti satthu thūpapūjākaraṇavasena pariccajitvā pariccāgahetu. 
646269,128,2418,22,41,1,167,16,"Asīti {vassakoṭiyo}ti manussagaṇanāya vassānaṃ asīti koṭiyo, accantasaṃyoge cetaṃ upayogavacanaṃ, idañca chasu kāmasaggesu dutiye aparāparuppattivasena vuttanti veditabbaṃ. "
