646272,128,2418,69,85,1,152,14,"Sesakenamhi {nibbuto}ti pupphapūjāya vasena pavattakusalacetanāsu bhavasampatti dāyakakammato sesena yaṃ tattha vivaṭṭūpanissayabhūtaṃ, taṃ sandhāya vadati. "
