646274,128,2418,93,107,1,128,12,"{Sesakenā}ti vā tasseva kammassa vipākāvasesena aparikkhīṇeyeva tasmiṃ kammavipāke nibbuto amhi, kilesaparinibbānena parinibbutosmi. "
