646512,128,2557,43,47,1,27,4,Tassa satthā dhammaṃ desesi. 
646513,128,2557,48,62,1,115,13,So dhammaṃ sutvā uḷāraṃ pītisomanassaṃ pavedento apphoṭento uṭṭhahitvā satthāraṃ vanditvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
