646536,128,2574,2,30,1,256,25,"Tattha lahuko vata me {kāyo}ti nīvaraṇādivikkhambhanena cuddasavidhena cittaparidamanena caturiddhipādakabhāvanāya suṭṭhu ciṇṇavasībhāvena ca me rūpakāyo sallahuko vata, yena dandhaṃ mahābhūtapaccayampi nāma imaṃ karajakāyaṃ cittavasena pariṇāmemīti adhippāyo. "
646537,128,2574,31,48,1,124,15,Phuṭṭho ca pītisukhena {vipulenā}ti sabbatthakameva pharantena mahatā uḷārena pītisahitena sukhena phuṭṭho ca me kāyoti yojanā. 
646538,128,2574,49,58,1,54,8,"Idañca yathā kāyo lahuko ahosi, taṃ dassanatthaṃ vuttaṃ. "
646539,128,2574,59,64,1,57,5,Sukhasaññokkamanena hi saddhiṃyeva lahusaññokkamanaṃ hoti. 
646540,128,2574,65,77,1,146,11,"Sukhassa pharaṇañcettha taṃsamuṭṭhānarūpavasena daṭṭhabbaṃ kathaṃ pana catutthajjhānasamaṅgino pītisukhapharaṇaṃ, samatikkantapītisukhañhi tanti ce? "
646541,128,2574,78,89,1,85,9,"Saccametaṃ, idaṃ pana na catutthajjhānalakkhaṇavasena vuttaṃ, atha kho pubbabhāgavasena."
646542,128,2574,90,108,1,119,13,"‘‘ Pītisukhenā’’ ti pana pītisahitasadisena sukhena, upekkhā hi idha santasabhāvatāya ñāṇavisesayogato ca sukhanti adhippetaṃ. "
646543,128,2574,109,129,1,54,7,Tathā hi vuttaṃ‘‘ sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca okkamatī’’ ti( paṭi. ma.1.101). 
646544,128,2574,130,145,1,152,14,Pādakajjhānārammaṇena rūpakāyārammaṇena vā iddhicittena sahajātaṃ sukhasaññañca lahusaññañca okkamati pavisati phusati sampāpuṇātīti ayampi tattha attho. 
646545,128,2574,146,162,1,24,3,Tathā cāha aṭṭhakathāyaṃ( paṭi. ma. aṭṭha.2.3.12)–
646546,128,2574,163,169,1,39,4,‘‘ sukhasaññā nāma upekkhāsampayuttā saññā. 
646547,128,2574,170,184,1,121,14,Upekkhā hi santaṃ sukhanti vuttaṃ sāyeva saññā nīvaraṇehi ceva vitakkādipaccanīkehi ca vimuttattā lahusaññātipi veditabbā. 
646548,128,2574,185,193,1,64,8,Taṃ okkantassa panassa karajakāyopi tūlapicu viya sallahuko hoti. 
646549,128,2574,194,206,1,89,10,So evaṃ vātakkhittatūlapicuno viya sallahukena dissamānena kāyena brahmalokaṃ gacchatī’’ ti. 
646550,128,2574,207,220,1,53,8,"Tenāha‘‘ tūlamiva eritaṃ mālutena, pilavatīva me kāyo’’ ti. "
646551,128,2574,221,243,1,146,20,"Tassattho– yadāhaṃ brahmalokaṃ aññaṃ vā iddhiyā gantukāmo homi, tadā mālutena vāyunā eritaṃ cittaṃ tūlapicu viya ākāsaṃ laṅghantoyeva me kāyo hotīti. "
646552,128,2575,2,4,1,34,2,Khitakattheragāthāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
646553,128,2576,2,4,1,30,2,5 . Malitavambhattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
646554,128,2577,2,8,1,49,4,{Ukkaṇṭhito}ti āyasmato malitavambhattherassa gāthā. 
646555,128,2577,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646556,128,2577,12,33,1,179,20,"Ayaṃ kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle himavantato avidūre aññatarasmiṃ jātassare sakuṇo hutvā nibbatti, padumuttaro bhagavā taṃ anuggaṇhanto tattha gantvā jātassaratīre caṅkamati. "
646557,128,2577,34,43,1,79,9,Sakuṇo bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso sare kumudāni gahetvā bhagavantaṃ pūjesi. 
646558,128,2577,44,62,1,158,17,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kurukacchanagare aññatarassa brāhmaṇassa putto hutvā nibbatti, malitavambho tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
646559,128,2577,63,78,1,143,15,So viññutaṃ patto pacchābhūmahātheraṃ upasaṅkamitvā tassa santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto viharati. 
646560,128,2577,79,94,1,84,12,"Tassa ca ayaṃ sabhāvo, yattha bhojanasappāyo dullabho, itare sulabhā, tato na pakkamati. "
646561,128,2577,95,107,1,78,10,"Yattha pana bhojanasappāyo sulabho, itare dullabhā, tattha na vasati pakkamateva. "
646562,128,2577,108,120,1,108,11,Evaṃ viharanto ca hetusampannatāya mahāpurisajātikatāya ca nacirasseva vipassanaṃ vaḍḍhetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
646563,128,2577,121,134,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.16.51-57)–
646564,128,2578,2,9,1,36,4,"‘ ‘ Himavantassāvidūre , mahājātassaro ahu; "
646565,128,2579,2,5,1,40,2,"Padumuppalasañchanno , puṇḍarīkasamotthaṭo."
646566,128,2580,2,11,1,42,7,"‘ ‘ Kukuttho nāma nāmena, tatthāsiṃ sakuṇo tadā; "
646567,128,2581,2,7,1,41,4,"Sīlavā buddhisampanno, puññāpuññesu kovido."
646568,128,2582,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Padumuttaro lokavidū, āhutīnaṃ paṭiggaho; "
646569,128,2583,2,6,1,39,3,"Jātassarassāvidūre , sañcarittha mahāmuni."
646570,128,2584,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Jalajaṃ kumudaṃ chetvā, upanesiṃ mahesino; "
646571,128,2585,2,7,1,39,4,"Mama saṅkappamaññāya, paṭiggahi mahāmuni."
646572,128,2586,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Tañca dānaṃ daditvāna, sukkamūlena codito; "
646573,128,2587,2,7,1,43,4,"Kappānaṃ satasahassaṃ, duggatiṃ nupapajjahaṃ."
646574,128,2588,2,9,1,36,5,"‘ ‘ Soḷaseto kappasate, āsuṃ varuṇanāmakā; "
646575,128,2589,2,8,1,40,5,"Aṭṭha ete janādhipā, cakkavattī mahabbalā."
646576,128,2590,2,16,1,51,9,‘ ‘ Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ… pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti. 
646577,128,2591,2,9,1,62,7,Arahattaṃ pana patvā attano paṭipattiṃ paccavekkhitvā udānento– 
646578,128,2592,2,4,1,0,0,105.
646579,128,2593,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Ukkaṇṭhitopi na vase, ramamānopi pakkame; "
646580,128,2594,2,11,1,47,6,"Na tvevānatthasaṃhitaṃ, vase vāsaṃ vicakkhaṇo’’ ti."
646581,128,2594,12,15,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
646582,128,2595,2,26,1,205,22,"Tattha ukkaṇṭhitopi na {vase}ti yasmiṃ āvāse vasantassa me bhojanasappāyālābhena adhikusalesu dhammesu ukkaṇṭhā anabhirati uppajjati, tattha ukkaṇṭhitopi vasāmiyeva itarasappāyalābhena na pakkame na pakkamāmi. "
646583,128,2595,27,34,1,57,6,Na {vase}ti ettha na-kārenapi pakkametipadaṃ sambandhitabbaṃ. 
646584,128,2595,35,59,1,179,19,"Ramamānopi {pakkame}ti yasmiṃ pana āvāse vasantassa me paccayavekallābhāvena natthi ukkaṇṭhā, aññadatthu abhiramāmi, evaṃ abhiramamānopi avasesasappāyālābhena tato pakkame, na vaseyyaṃ. "
646585,128,2595,60,65,1,57,5,Evaṃ paṭipajjantovāhaṃ nacirasseva sakatthaṃ paccupādinti. 
646586,128,2595,66,69,1,47,3,Ayañcettha attapaṭipattipaccavekkhaṇāyaṃ yojanā. 
646587,128,2595,70,79,1,71,8,Parassa ovādadāne pana vaseyya na pakkameyyāti vidhānavasena yojetabbaṃ. 
646588,128,2595,80,115,1,240,28,"Na tvevānatthasaṃhitaṃ, vase vāsaṃ {vicakkhaṇo}ti yasmiṃ āvāse paccayā sulabhā , samaṇadhammo na pāripūriṃ gacchati, yasmiñca āvāse paccayā dullabhā, samaṇadhammopi pāripūriṃ na gacchati, evarūpo āvāso idha anatthasaṃhito nāma avaḍḍhisahitoti katvā. "
646589,128,2595,116,124,1,78,8,Evarūpaṃ vāsaṃ vicakkhaṇo viññujātiko sakatthaṃ paripūretukāmo natveva vaseyya. 
646590,128,2595,125,138,1,97,11,"Yattha pana pañcaṅgasamannāgato āvāso labbhati, sattapi sappāyā labbhanti, tattheva vaseyyāti attho. "
