646592,128,2597,2,4,1,27,2,6 . Suhemantattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
646593,128,2598,2,8,1,57,5,Sataliṅgassa {atthassā}ti āyasmato suhemantattherassa gāthā. 
646594,128,2598,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646595,128,2598,12,43,1,252,30,"Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto ito dvānavute kappe tissassa bhagavato kāle vanacaro hutvā vane vasati, taṃ anuggahituṃ bhagavā araññaṃ pavisitvā tassa āsanne ṭhāne aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi. "
646596,128,2598,44,53,1,88,9,So bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannacitto sugandhāni punnāgapupphāni ocinitvā bhagavantaṃ pūjesi. 
646597,128,2598,54,77,1,205,22,"So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde pāriyantadese vibhavasampannassa brāhmaṇassa putto hutvā nibbatti, suhemanto tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
646598,128,2598,78,99,1,206,20,So viññutaṃ patto saṅkassanagare migadāye viharantaṃ bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā tepiṭako hutvā vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva chaḷabhiñño paṭisambhidāpatto ahosi. 
646599,128,2598,100,113,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.16.46-50)–
646600,128,2599,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Kānanaṃ vanamogayha, vasāmi luddako ahaṃ; "
646601,128,2600,2,8,1,48,5,"Punnāgaṃ pupphitaṃ disvā, buddhaseṭṭhaṃ anussariṃ."
646602,128,2601,2,12,1,49,7,"‘ ‘ Taṃ pupphaṃ ocinitvāna, sugandhaṃ gandhitaṃ subhaṃ; "
646603,128,2602,2,8,1,43,5,"Thūpaṃ karitvā puline, buddhassa abhiropayiṃ."
646604,128,2603,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Dvenavute ito kappe, yaṃ pupphamabhipūjayiṃ; "
646605,128,2604,2,7,1,43,4,"Duggatiṃ nābhijānāmi, buddhapūjāyidaṃ phalaṃ."
