646611,128,2608,29,51,1,209,22,Evaṃ cintetvā pabhinnapaṭisambhidatāya akilāsutāya ca attano santikaṃ upagate bhikkhū yathārahaṃ ovadanto anusāsanto kaṅkhaṃ chindanto dhammaṃ kathento kammaṭṭhānaṃ niggumbaṃ nijjaṭaṃ katvā ācikkhanto viharati. 
646612,128,2608,52,61,1,92,9,Athekadivasaṃ attano santikaṃ upagatānaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ viññūnañca puggalānaṃ visesaṃ ācikkhanto– 
646613,128,2609,2,4,1,0,0,106.
646614,128,2610,2,8,1,41,4,"‘ ‘ Sataliṅgassa atthassa, satalakkhaṇadhārino; "
646615,128,2611,2,11,1,44,6,"Ekaṅgadassī dummedho, satadassī ca paṇḍito’’ ti."
646616,128,2611,12,15,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
646617,128,2612,2,20,1,136,15,"Tattha {sataliṅgassā}ti līnamatthaṃ gamentīti liṅgāni, atthesu saddassa pavattinimittāni, tāni pana sataṃ anekāni liṅgāni etassāti sataliṅgo. "
646618,128,2612,21,38,1,96,12,"Anekattho hi idha satasaddo,‘‘ sataṃ sahassan’’ tiādīsu viya na saṅkhyāvisesattho tassa sataliṅgassa. "
646619,128,2612,39,53,1,62,8,"{Atthassā}ti ñeyyassa, ñeyyañhi ñāṇena araṇīyato‘‘ attho’’ ti vuccati. "
646620,128,2612,54,79,1,85,15,"So ca ekopi anekaliṅgo, yathā‘‘ sakko purindado maghavā’’ ti,‘‘ paññā vijjā medhā ñāṇan’’ ti ca. "
646621,128,2612,80,96,1,119,14,"Yena liṅgena pavattinimittena tāvatiṃsādhipatimhi indasaddo pavatto, na tena tattha sakkādisaddā pavattā, atha kho aññena. "
646622,128,2612,97,106,1,65,8,"Tathā yena sammādiṭṭhimhi paññāsaddo pavatto, na tena vijjādisaddā. "
646623,128,2612,107,116,1,36,5,Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ sataliṅgassa atthassā’’ ti. 
646624,128,2613,2,6,1,39,2,{Satalakkhaṇadhārino}ti anekalakkhaṇavato. 
646625,128,2613,7,25,1,131,16,"Lakkhīyati etenāti lakkhaṇaṃ, paccayabhāvino atthassa attano phalaṃ paṭicca paccayabhāvo, tena hi so ayaṃ imassa kāraṇanti lakkhīyati. "
646626,128,2613,26,41,1,79,9,"So ca ekasseva atthassa anekappabhedo upalabbhati , tenāha‘‘ satalakkhaṇadhārino’’ ti. "
646627,128,2613,42,57,1,121,14,"Atha vā lakkhīyantīti lakkhaṇāni, tassa tassa atthassa saṅkhatatādayo pakāravisesā te pana atthato avatthāvisesā veditabbā. "
646628,128,2613,58,73,1,85,11,Te ca pana tesaṃ aniccatādisāmaññalakkhaṇaṃ liṅgenti ñāpentīti‘‘ liṅgānī’’ ti ca vuccanti. 
646629,128,2613,74,82,1,56,7,"Tassime ākārā, yasmā ekassāpi atthassa aneke upalabbhanti. "
646630,128,2613,83,94,1,56,6,"Tena vuttaṃ‘‘ sataliṅgassa atthassa, satalakkhaṇadhārino’’ ti. "
646631,128,2613,95,98,1,28,3,Tenāha āyasmā dhammasenāpati–
646632,128,2613,99,130,1,76,9,‘‘ sabbe dhammā sabbākārena buddhassa bhagavato ñāṇamukhe āpāthaṃ āgacchantī’’ ti( mahāni.156; cūḷani. mogharājamāṇavapucchāniddesa85; paṭi. ma.3.5). 
646633,128,2614,2,48,1,350,35,"Ekaṅgadassī {dummedho}ti evaṃ anekaliṅge anekalakkhaṇe atthe yo tattha ekaṅgadassī aputhupaññatāya ekaliṅgamattaṃ ekalakkhaṇamattañca disvā attanā diṭṭhameva‘‘ idameva saccan’’ ti abhinivissa ‘‘ moghamaññan’’ ti itaraṃ paṭikkhipati, hatthidassanakaandho viya ekaṅgagāhī dummedho duppañño tattha vijjamānānaṃyeva pakāravisesānaṃ ajānanato micchā abhinivisanato ca. "
646634,128,2614,49,63,1,104,13,Satadassī ca {paṇḍito}ti paṇḍito pana tattha vijjamāne anekepi pakāre attano paññācakkhunā sabbaso passati. 
646635,128,2614,64,83,1,131,17,"Yo vā tattha labbhamāne aneke paññācakkhunā attanāpi passati, aññesampi dasseti pakāseti, so paṇḍito vicakkhaṇo atthesu kusalo nāmāti. "
