646925,128,2778,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Tārako tvaṃ yathā nāvā, nidhīvassāsakārako; "
646926,128,2779,2,8,1,39,5,"Asambhīto yathā sīho, gajarājāva dappito."
646927,128,2780,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Thometvā dasagāthāhi, padumuttaraṃ mahāyasaṃ; "
646928,128,2781,2,9,1,44,6,"Vanditvā satthuno pāde, tuṇhī aṭṭhāsahaṃ tadā."
646929,128,2782,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Padumuttaro lokavidū, āhutīnaṃ paṭiggaho; "
646930,128,2783,2,9,1,46,6,"Bhikkhusaṅghe ṭhito satthā, imā gāthā abhāsatha."
646931,128,2784,2,11,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Yo me sīlañca ñāṇañca, saddhammañcāpi vaṇṇayi; "
646932,128,2785,2,8,1,41,5,"Tamahaṃ kittayissāmi, suṇātha mama bhāsato."
646933,128,2786,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Saṭṭhi kappasahassāni, devaloke ramissati; "
646934,128,2787,2,7,1,40,4,"Aññe devebhibhavitvā, issaraṃ kārayissati."
