646936,128,2789,2,7,1,39,4,"Gotamassa bhagavato, sāsane pabbajissati."
646937,128,2790,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Pabbajitvāna kāyena, pāpakammaṃ vivajjiya; "
