646940,128,2793,2,9,1,44,6,"Tatheva tvaṃ mahāvīra, dhammena tappayī mamaṃ."
646941,128,2794,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Sīlaṃ paññañca dhammañca, thavitvā lokanāyakaṃ; "
646942,128,2795,2,8,1,45,5,"Pattomhi paramaṃ santiṃ, nibbānaṃ padamaccutaṃ."
646943,128,2796,2,12,1,44,8,"‘ ‘ Aho nūna sa bhagavā, ciraṃ tiṭṭheyya cakkhumā; "
646944,128,2797,2,8,1,43,5,"Aññātañca vijāneyyuṃ, phuseyyuṃ amataṃ padaṃ."
646945,128,2798,2,12,1,42,8,"‘ ‘ Ayaṃ me pacchimā jāti, bhavā sabbe samūhatā; "
646946,128,2799,2,7,1,36,4,"Sabbāsave pariññāya, viharāmi anāsavo."
646947,128,2800,2,9,1,43,5,"‘ ‘ Satasahassito kappe, yaṃ buddhamabhithomayiṃ; "
646948,128,2801,2,8,1,42,5,"Duggatiṃ nābhijānāmi, kittanāya idaṃ phalaṃ."
