646951,128,2804,2,4,1,0,0,114.
646952,128,2805,2,8,1,39,4,"‘ ‘ Kāyaduṭṭhullagaruno, hiyyamānamhi jīvite; "
646953,128,2806,2,9,1,42,4,"Sarīrasukhagiddhassa , kuto samaṇasādhutā’’ ti."
646954,128,2806,10,13,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
646955,128,2807,2,27,1,237,20,"Tattha {kāyaduṭṭhullagaruno}ti duṭṭhullaṃ asubhayogyatā, kāyassa duṭṭhullaṃ kāyaduṭṭhullaṃ, kāyaduṭṭhullaṃ garu sambhāvitaṃ yassa so kāyaduṭṭhullagaru, anissaraṇappañño hutvā kāyaposanappasuto kāyadaḷhibahuloti attho, tassa kāyaduṭṭhullagaruno. "
646956,128,2807,28,37,1,76,8,Hiyyamānamhi {jīvite}ti kunnadīnaṃ udakaṃ viya jīvitasaṅkhāre lahuso khīyamāne. 
646957,128,2807,38,47,1,77,7,{Sarīrasukhagiddhassā}ti paṇītāhārādīhi attano kāyassa sukhena gedhaṃ āpannassa . 
646958,128,2807,48,72,1,219,22,"Kuto {samaṇasādhutā}ti evarūpassa puggalassa samaṇabhāvena sādhutā susamaṇatā kuto kena kāraṇena siyā, ekaṃsato pana kāye jīvite ca nirapekkhassa itarītarasantosena santuṭṭhassa āraddhavīriyasseva samaṇasādhutāti adhippāyo. "
