646960,128,2809,2,4,1,26,2,5 . Mahānāmattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
646961,128,2810,2,9,1,57,5,Esāvahiyyase {pabbatenā}ti āyasmato mahānāmattherassa gāthā. 
646962,128,2810,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
646963,128,2810,13,41,1,254,28,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā brāhmaṇavijjāsu nipphattiṃ gato gharāvāsaṃ pahāya aññatarāya nadiyā tīre assamaṃ kāretvā sambahule brāhmaṇe mante vācento viharati. 
646964,128,2810,42,49,1,65,7,Athekadivasaṃ bhagavā taṃ anuggaṇhituṃ tassa asamapadaṃ upagacchi. 
646965,128,2810,50,58,1,57,7,So bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannacitto āsanaṃ paññāpetvā adāsi . 
646966,128,2810,59,64,1,45,5,Nisinne bhagavati sumadhuraṃ madhuṃ upanāmesi. 
646967,128,2810,65,74,1,97,9,Taṃ bhagavā paribhuñjitvā heṭṭhā adhimuttattheravatthumhi vuttanayena anāgataṃ byākaritvā pakkāmi. 
646968,128,2810,75,137,1,505,53,So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ sugatīsuyeva parivattento imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {mahānāmo}ti laddhanāmo viññutaṃ patto bhagavato santikaṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā nesādake nāma pabbate viharanto kilesapariyuṭṭhānaṃ vikkhambhetuṃ asakkonto‘‘ kiṃ me iminā saṃkiliṭṭhacittassa jīvitenā’’ ti attabhāvaṃ nibbindanto uccaṃ pabbatasikharaṃ abhiruhitvā‘‘ ito pātetvā taṃ māressāmī’’ ti attānaṃ paraṃ viya niddisanto– 
646969,128,2811,2,4,1,0,0,115.
646970,128,2812,2,8,1,44,4,"‘ ‘ Esāvahiyyase pabbatena, bahukuṭajasallakikena; "
646971,128,2813,2,10,1,43,5,"Nesādakena girinā, yasassinā paricchadenā’’ ti."
646972,128,2813,11,14,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
646973,128,2814,2,11,1,61,7,Tattha {esāvahiyyase}ti eso tvaṃ mahānāma avahiyyase parihāyasi. 
646974,128,2814,12,17,1,47,4,{Pabbatenā}ti nivāsaṭṭhānabhūtena iminā pabbatena. 
646975,128,2814,18,27,1,100,8,{Bahukuṭajasallakikenā}ti bahūhi kuṭajehi indasālarukkhehi sallakīhi indasālarukkhehi vā samannāgatena. 
646976,128,2814,28,31,1,25,2,{Nesādakenā}ti evaṃnāmakena. 
646977,128,2814,32,35,1,15,2,{Girinā}ti selena. 
646978,128,2814,36,61,1,137,15,"Selo hi sandhisaṅkhātehi pabbehi ṭhitattā‘‘ pabbato’’ ti, pasavanādivasena jalassa, sārabhūtānaṃ bhesajjādivatthūnañca giraṇato‘‘ girī’’ ti vuccati. "
646979,128,2814,62,79,1,71,9,Tadubhayatthasambhavato panettha‘‘ pabbatenā’’ ti vatvā‘‘ girinā’’ ti ca vuttaṃ. 
646980,128,2814,80,85,1,42,4,{Yasassinā}ti sabbaguṇehi vissutena pakāsena. 
646981,128,2814,86,96,1,106,8,"{Paricchadenā}ti nānāvidharukkhagacchalatāhi samantato channena, vasanaṭṭhānatāya vā tuyhaṃ paricchadabhūtena. "
646982,128,2814,97,129,1,250,26,"Ayañhettha adhippāyo– mahānāma, yadi kammaṭṭhānaṃ vissajjetvā vitakkabahulo hosi, evaṃ tvaṃ iminā chāyūdakasampannena sappāyena nivāsanaṭṭhānabhūtena nesādakagirinā parihāyasi, idānihaṃ taṃ ito pātetvā māressāmi, tasmā na labbhā vitakkavasikena bhavitunti. "
646983,128,2814,130,139,1,75,8,Evaṃ thero attānaṃ santajjentoyeva vipassanaṃ ussukkāpetvā arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
646984,128,2814,140,153,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.40.333-352)–
646985,128,2815,2,11,1,39,7,"‘ ‘ Sindhuyā nadiyā tīre, sukato assamo mama; "
