647022,128,2852,2,4,1,28,2,6 . Pārāpariyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
647023,128,2853,2,9,1,58,5,Chaphassāyatane {hitvā}ti āyasmato pārāpariyattherassa gāthā. 
647024,128,2853,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
647025,128,2853,13,39,1,261,26,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto piyadassissa bhagavato kāle nesādayoniyaṃ nibbattitvā tassa viññutaṃ pattassa vicaraṇaṭṭhāne aññatarasmiṃ vanasaṇḍe piyadassī bhagavā taṃ anuggaṇhituṃ nirodhasamāpattiṃ samāpajjitvā nisīdi. 
647026,128,2853,40,64,1,219,24,So ca mige pariyesanto taṃ ṭhānaṃ gato satthāraṃ disvā pasannamānaso bhagavantaṃ anto katvā kataṃ sākhāmaṇḍapaṃ padumapupphehi kūṭāgārākārena sañchādetvā uḷāraṃ pītisomanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedento sattāhaṃ namassamāno aṭṭhāsi. 
647027,128,2853,65,72,1,59,7,Divase divase ca milātamilātāni apanetvā abhinavehi chādesi. 
647028,128,2853,73,80,1,72,7,Satthā sattāhassa accayena nirodhato vuṭṭhahitvā bhikkhusaṅghaṃ anussari. 
647029,128,2853,81,86,1,56,5,Tāvadeva asītisahassamattā bhikkhū satthāraṃ parivāresuṃ.
647030,128,2853,87,100,1,72,8,"‘‘ Madhuradhammakathaṃ suṇissāmā’’ ti devatā sannipatiṃsu, mahā samāgamo ahosi. "
647031,128,2853,101,113,1,118,12,Satthā anumodanaṃ karonto tassa devamanussesu bhāviniṃ sampattiṃ imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvakabodhiñca byākaritvā pakkāmi. 
647032,128,2853,114,151,1,342,35,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū hutvā parāparagottatāya {pārāpariyo}ti laddhasamañño bahū brāhmaṇe mante vācento satthu rājagahagamane buddhānubhāvaṃ disvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
647033,128,2853,152,165,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.40.353-385)–
647034,128,2854,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Piyadassī nāma bhagavā, sayambhū lokanāyako; "
647035,128,2855,2,7,1,39,4,"Vivekakāmo sambuddho, samādhikusalo muni."
647036,128,2856,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Vanasaṇḍaṃ samoggayha, piyadassī mahāmuni; "
647037,128,2857,2,7,1,41,4,"Paṃsukūlaṃ pattharitvā, nisīdi purisuttamo."
647038,128,2858,2,11,1,38,7,"‘ ‘ Migaluddo pure āsiṃ, araññe kānane ahaṃ; "
647039,128,2859,2,8,1,38,5,"Pasadaṃ migamesanto, āhiṇḍāmi ahaṃ tadā."
