647043,128,2863,2,8,1,41,5,"Jātassaraṃ samoggayha, padumaṃ āhariṃ tadā."
647044,128,2864,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Āharitvāna padumaṃ, satapattaṃ manoramaṃ; "
647045,128,2865,2,7,1,40,4,"Kūṭāgāraṃ karitvāna, chādayiṃ padumenahaṃ."
