647070,128,2890,2,9,1,39,5,"‘ ‘ Tathevīmassa ñāṇamhi, kilesā nopalimpare; "
647071,128,2891,2,8,1,39,5,"Manasā vinivaṭṭetvā, pañca nīvaraṇe ayaṃ."
647072,128,2892,2,10,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Cittaṃ janetvā nekkhamme, agārā pabbajissati; "
647073,128,2893,2,8,1,45,5,"Tato pupphamaye byamhe, dhārente nikkhamissati."
647074,128,2894,2,9,1,40,5,"‘ ‘ Rukkhamūle vasantassa, nipakassa satīmato; "
647075,128,2895,2,8,1,48,5,"Tattha pupphamayaṃ byamhaṃ, matthake dhārayissati."
647076,128,2896,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Cīvaraṃ piṇḍapātañca, paccayaṃ sayanāsanaṃ; "
647077,128,2897,2,6,1,43,3,"Datvāna bhikkhusaṅghassa, nibbāyissatināsavo."
647078,128,2898,2,9,1,41,5,"‘ ‘ Kūṭāgārena caratā, pabbajjaṃ abhinikkhamiṃ; "
647079,128,2899,2,7,1,41,4,"Rukkhamūle vasantampi, kūṭāgāraṃ dharīyati."
647080,128,2900,2,12,1,40,8,"‘ ‘ Cīvare piṇḍapāte ca, cetanā me na vijjati; "
647081,128,2901,2,7,1,43,4,"Puññakammena saṃyutto, labhāmi pariniṭṭhitaṃ."
647082,128,2902,2,10,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Gaṇanāto asaṅkheyyā, kappakoṭī bahū mama; "
647083,128,2903,2,8,1,39,5,"Rittakā te atikkantā, pamuttā lokanāyakā."
647084,128,2904,2,9,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Aṭṭhārase kappasate, piyadassī vināyako; "
647085,128,2905,2,8,1,40,5,"Tamahaṃ payirupāsitvā, imaṃ yoniṃ upāgato."
647086,128,2906,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Idha passāmi sambuddhaṃ, anomaṃ nāma cakkhumaṃ; "
647087,128,2907,2,7,1,39,4,"Tamahaṃ upagantvāna, pabbajiṃ anagāriyaṃ."
647088,128,2908,2,11,1,45,7,"‘ ‘ Dukkhassantakaro buddho, maggaṃ me desayī jino; "
647089,128,2909,2,9,1,45,6,"Tassa dhammaṃ suṇitvāna, pattomhi acalaṃ padaṃ."
