647097,128,2917,2,10,1,42,5,"‘ ‘ Chaphassāyatane hitvā, guttadvāro susaṃvuto; "
647098,128,2918,2,11,1,43,6,"Aghamūlaṃ vamitvāna, patto me āsavakkhayo’’ ti."
647099,128,2918,12,15,1,13,2,– gāthaṃ abhāsi; 
647100,128,2919,2,22,1,198,15,Tattha chaphassāyatane {hitvā}ti cakkhusamphassādīnaṃ channaṃ samphassānaṃ uppattiṭṭhānatāya‘‘ phassāyatanānī’’ ti laddhanāmāni cakkhādīni cha ajjhattikāyatanāni tappaṭibaddhasaṃkilesappahānavasena pahāya. 
647101,128,2919,23,41,1,176,16,"Guttadvāro {susaṃvuto}ti tato eva cakkhudvārādīnaṃ guttattā, tattha pavattanakānaṃ abhijjhādīnaṃ pāpadhammānaṃ pavesananivāraṇena satikavāṭena suṭṭu pihitattā guttadvāro susaṃvuto. "
647102,128,2919,42,58,1,140,15,"Atha vā manacchaṭṭhānaṃ channaṃ dvārānaṃ vuttanayena rakkhitattā guttadvāro, kāyādīhi suṭṭhu saññatattā susaṃvutoti evamettha attho veditabbo. "
647103,128,2919,59,79,1,193,17,"Aghamūlaṃ {vamitvānā}ti aghassa vaṭṭadukkhassa mūlabhūtaṃ avijjābhavataṇhāsaṅkhātaṃ dosaṃ, sabbaṃ vā kilesadosaṃ ariyamaggasaṅkhātavamanayogapānena uggiritvā santānato bahi katvā, bahikaraṇahetu vā. "
647104,128,2919,80,97,1,117,14,"Patto me {āsavakkhayo}ti kāmāsavādayo āsavā ettha khīyanti, tesaṃ vā khayena pattabboti āsavakkhayo, nibbānaṃ arahattañca. "
647105,128,2919,98,105,1,57,7,So āsavakkhayo patto adhigatoti udānavasena aññaṃ byākāsi. 
647106,128,2920,2,4,1,37,2,Pārāpariyattheragāthāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
647107,128,2921,2,4,1,22,2,7 . Yasattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
647108,128,2922,2,10,1,49,5,Suvilitto {suvasano}ti āyasmato yasattherassa gāthā. 
647109,128,2922,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
647110,128,2922,14,36,1,217,22,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayāni puññāni upacinanto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle mahānubhāvo nāgarājā hutvā buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ attano bhavanaṃ netvā mahādānaṃ pavattesi. 
647111,128,2922,37,49,1,132,11,"Bhagavantaṃ mahagghena ticīvarena acchādesi, ekamekañca bhikkhuṃ mahaggheneva paccekadussayugena sabbena samaṇaparikkhārena acchādesi. "
647112,128,2922,50,64,1,132,14,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto siddhatthassa bhagavato kāle seṭṭhiputto hutvā mahābodhimaṇḍaṃ sattahi ratanehi pūjesi. 
647113,128,2922,65,72,1,63,7,Kassapassa bhagavato kāle sāsane pabbajitvā samaṇadhammaṃ akāsi. 
647114,128,2922,73,91,1,149,17,"Evaṃ sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ amhākaṃ bhagavato kāle bārāṇasiyaṃ mahāvibhavassa seṭṭhino putto hutvā nibbatti, yaso nāma nāmena paramasukhumālo."
647115,128,2922,92,109,1,60,8,‘‘ Tassa tayo pāsādā’’ ti sabbaṃ khandhake( mahāva.25) āgatanayena veditabbaṃ. 
647116,128,2923,2,35,1,243,25,"So pubbahetunā codiyamāno rattibhāge niddābhibhūtassa parijanassa vippakāraṃ disvā sañjātasaṃvego suvaṇṇapādukārūḷhova gehato niggato devatāvivaṭena nagaradvārena nikkhamitvā isipatanasamīpaṃ gato‘‘ upaddutaṃ vata, bho, upassaṭṭhaṃ vata, bho’’ ti āha. "
647117,128,2923,36,93,1,438,45,"Tena samayena bhagavatā isipatane viharantena tasseva anuggaṇhanatthaṃ abbhokāse caṅkamantena‘‘ ehi, yasa, idaṃ anupaddutaṃ, idaṃ anupassaṭṭhan’’ ti vutto,‘‘ anupaddutaṃ anupassaṭṭhaṃ kira atthī’’ ti somanassajāto suvaṇṇapādukā oruyha bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisinno satthārā anupubbikathaṃ kathetvā saccadesanāya katāya saccapariyosāne sotāpanno hutvā gavesanatthaṃ āgatassa pitu bhagavatā saccadesanāya kariyamānāya arahattaṃ sacchākāsi. "
647118,128,2923,94,107,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera1.40.456-483)–
