647183,128,2981,2,4,1,24,2,8 . Kimilattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
647184,128,2982,2,8,1,53,5,Abhisattova {nipatatī}ti āyasmato kimilattherassa gāthā. 
647185,128,2982,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
647186,128,2982,12,36,1,216,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni karonto kakusandhassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto parinibbute satthari tassa dhātuyo uddissa saḷalamālāhi maṇḍapākārena pūjaṃ akāsi. 
647187,128,2982,37,55,1,166,17,"So tena puññakammena tāvatiṃse nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kapilavatthunagare sākiyarājakule nibbatti, kimilo tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
647188,128,2982,56,61,1,47,5,So vayappatto bhogasampattiyā sampanno viharati. 
647189,128,2982,62,85,1,217,22,"Tassa ñāṇaparipākaṃ disvā saṃvegajananatthaṃ anupiyāyaṃ viharanto satthā paṭhamayobbane ṭhitaṃ dassanīyaṃ itthirūpaṃ abhinimminitvā purato dassetvā puna anukkamena yathā jarārogavipattīhi abhibhūtā dissati, tathā akāsi. "
647190,128,2982,86,92,1,49,6,Taṃ disvā kimilakumāro ativiya saṃvegaṃ pakāsento– 
