647200,128,2987,62,73,1,83,10,"Idha panassa yobbaññaṃ adhippetaṃ, taṃ hissa abhipatantaṃ khīyantaṃ hutvā upaṭṭhitaṃ. "
647201,128,2987,74,78,1,29,4,Rūpan ti rūpasampadāti vadati. 
647202,128,2987,79,109,1,131,17,Rūpan ti pana sarīraṃ‘‘ aṭṭhiñca paṭicca nhāruñca paṭicca maṃsañca paṭicca ākāso parivārito rūpaṃtveva saṅkhaṃ gacchatī’’ tiādīsu( ma. ni.1.306) viya. 
647203,128,2987,110,128,1,130,17,"Aññamiva tatheva santan ti idaṃ rūpaṃ yādisaṃ, sayaṃ tatheva tenevākārena santaṃ vijjamānaṃ aññaṃ viya mayhaṃ upaṭṭhātīti adhippāyo."
647204,128,2987,129,139,1,33,6,‘‘ Tadeva santan’’ ti ca keci paṭhanti. 
647205,128,2987,140,148,1,50,7,Tasseva {sato}ti tasseva me anaññassa sato samānassa. 
647206,128,2987,149,165,1,119,14,"{Avippavasato}ti na vippavasantassa, ciravippavāsena hi sato anaññampi aññaṃ viya upaṭṭhāti idampi idha natthīti adhippāyo. "
647207,128,2987,166,180,1,106,14,Aññasseva sarāmi attānan ti imaṃ mama attabhāvaṃ aññassa sattassa viya sarāmi upadhāremi sañjānāmīti attho. 
647208,128,2987,181,202,1,195,20,"Tassevaṃ aniccataṃ manasi karontassa daḷhataro saṃvego udapādi, so saṃvegajāto satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanaṃ paṭṭhapetvā nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. "
