647284,128,3035,2,4,1,24,2,1 . Uttarattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
647285,128,3036,2,14,1,72,8,Dukanipāte natthi koci bhavo {nicco}tiādikā āyasmato uttarattherassa gāthā. 
647286,128,3036,15,17,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
647287,128,3036,18,34,1,149,16,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave vivaṭṭūpanissayaṃ puññaṃ upacinanto sumedhassa bhagavato kāle vijjādharo hutvā ākāsena vicarati. 
647288,128,3036,35,47,1,122,12,Tena ca samayena satthā tassa anuggaṇhanatthaṃ vanantare aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle nisīdi chabbaṇṇabuddharaṃsiyo vissajjento. 
647289,128,3036,48,100,1,463,49,"So antalikkhena gacchanto bhagavantaṃ disvā pasannacitto ākāsato oruyha suvisuddhehi vipulehi kaṇikārapupphehi bhagavantaṃ pūjesi, pupphāni buddhānubhāvena satthu upari chattākārena aṭṭhaṃsu, so tena bhiyyosomattāya pasannacitto hutvā aparabhāge kālaṃ katvā tāvatiṃse nibbattitvā uḷāraṃ dibbasampattiṃ anubhavanto yāvatāyukaṃ tattha ṭhatvā tato cuto devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahe brāhmaṇamahāsālaputto hutvā nibbatti, uttaro tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
647290,128,3036,101,116,1,120,15,So viññutaṃ patto brāhmaṇavijjāsu nipphattiṃ gantvā jātiyā rūpena vijjāya vayena sīlācārena ca lokassa sambhāvanīyo jāto. 
647291,128,3036,117,130,1,110,13,Tassa taṃ sampattiṃ disvā vassakāro magadhamahāmatto attano dhītaraṃ dātukāmo hutvā attano adhippāyaṃ pavedesi. 
647292,128,3036,131,149,1,180,18,So nissaraṇajjhāsayatāya taṃ paṭikkhipitvā kālena kālaṃ dhammasenāpatiṃ payirupāsanto tassa santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vattasampanno hutvā theraṃ upaṭṭhahati. 
647293,128,3037,2,27,1,208,24,"Tena ca samayena therassa aññataro ābādho uppanno, tassa bhesajjatthāya uttaro sāmaṇero pātova pattacīvaramādāya vihārato nikkhanto antarāmagge taḷākassa tīre pattaṃ ṭhapetvā udakasamīpaṃ gantvā mukhaṃ dhovati. "
647294,128,3037,28,45,1,163,16,Atha aññataro umaṅgacoro ārakkhapurisehi anubaddho aggadvāreneva nagarato nikkhamitvā palāyanto attanā gahitaṃ ratanabhaṇḍikaṃ sāmaṇerassa patte pakkhipitvā palāyi. 
647295,128,3037,46,50,1,29,3,Sāmaṇero pattasamīpaṃ upagato. 
647296,128,3037,51,77,1,162,19,"Coraṃ anubandhantā rājapurisā sāmaṇerassa patte bhaṇḍikaṃ disvā,‘‘ ayaṃ coro, iminā coriyaṃ katan’’ ti sāmaṇeraṃ pacchābāhaṃ bandhitvā vassakārassa brāhmaṇassa dassesuṃ. "
647297,128,3037,78,87,1,72,9,Vassakāro ca tadā rañño vinicchaye niyutto hutvā chejjabhejjaṃ anusāsati. 
647298,128,3037,88,109,1,124,16,"So‘‘ pubbe mama vacanaṃ nādiyi, suddhapāsaṇḍiyesu pabbajī’’ ti ca baddhāghātattā kammaṃ asodhetvāva jīvantameva taṃ sūle uttāsesi. "
647299,128,3038,2,39,1,359,30,"Athassa bhagavā ñāṇaparipākaṃ oloketvā taṃ ṭhānaṃ gantvā vipphurantahatthanakhamaṇimayūkhasambhinnasitābhatāya paggharantajātihiṅgulakasuvaṇṇarasadhāraṃ viya jālāguṇṭhitamudutalunadīghaṅgulihatthaṃ uttarassa sīse ṭhapetvā,‘‘ uttara, idaṃ te purimakammassa phalaṃ uppannaṃ, tattha tayā paccavekkhaṇabalena adhivāsanā kātabbā’’ ti vatvā ajjhāsayānurūpaṃ dhammaṃ desesi. "
647300,128,3038,40,63,1,269,23,Uttaro amatābhisekasadisena satthu hatthasamphassena sañjātappasādasomanassatāya uḷāraṃ pītipāmojjaṃ paṭilabhitvā yathāparicitaṃ vipassanāmaggaṃ samārūḷho ñāṇassa paripākaṃ gatattā satthu ca desanāvilāsena tāvadeva maggapaṭipāṭiyā sabbakilese khepetvā chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
