647600,128,3236,2,13,1,48,8,"Magge paṭipadāyaṃ vā, kaṅkhā mayhaṃ na vijjatī’’ ti."
647601,128,3236,14,17,1,18,2,– gāthādvayaṃ abhāsi; 
647602,128,3237,2,8,1,25,4,Tattha {yadā}ti yasmiṃ kāle. 
647603,128,3237,9,13,1,25,4,Ahan ti attānaṃ niddisati. 
647604,128,3237,14,17,1,27,3,Dhamman ti catusaccadhammaṃ. 
647605,128,3237,18,21,1,16,3,Assosin ti suṇiṃ. 
647606,128,3237,22,28,1,67,5,{Satthuno}ti diṭṭhadhammikādiatthehi veneyyānaṃ sāsanaṭṭhena satthuno. 
647607,128,3237,29,32,1,19,3,Kaṅkhan ti saṃsayaṃ. 
647608,128,3237,33,37,1,55,4,Saṅkhatamasaṅkhatañca anavasesato jānanaṭṭhena sabbaññū. 
647609,128,3237,38,42,1,35,4,Kutocipi parājitā bhāvena aparājite. 
647610,128,3237,43,48,1,69,5,Veneyyasattānaṃ saṃsārakantārato nibbānaṃ paṭivāhanaṭṭhena satthavāhe. 
647611,128,3237,49,120,1,610,59,"Idaṃ vuttaṃ hoti– yato pabhuti ahaṃ satthuno dhammaṃ desentassa catusacca dhammaṃ assosiṃ sotadvārānusārena upadhāresiṃ upalabhiṃ, tato paṭṭhāya anavasesasaṅkhatāsaṅkhatasammutidhammānaṃ sayambhūñāṇena jānanato sabbaññū anāvaraṇadassāvimhi, pañcannampi mārānaṃ abhibhavanato tehi aparājitattā sadevake loke appaṭihatadhammacakkattā ca aparājite, veneyyasattānaṃ lobhakantārādito vāhanaṭṭhena satthavāhe, mahāvikkantatāya mahāvīre, aññehi duddamānaṃ purisadammānaṃ saraṇato accantikena damathena damanato sārathīnaṃ pavarabhūte uttame sammāsambuddhe ,‘‘ buddho nu kho no nu kho’’ ti kaṅkhaṃ nābhijānāmi aparappaccayabhāvato. "
647612,128,3237,121,145,1,135,20,Tathārūpe desite ariya magge tadupādāyabhūtāya ca sīlādi paṭipadāya‘‘ niyyāniko nu kho na nu kho’’ ti kaṅkhā vicikicchā na vijjati natthīti. 
