647642,128,3250,2,11,1,59,7,Khīṇā hi mayhaṃ {jātī}tiādikā āyasmato surādhattherassa gāthā. 
647643,128,3250,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
647644,128,3250,15,36,1,195,21,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto sikhissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ satthāraṃ disvā pasannamānaso mātuluṅgaphalaṃ adāsi. 
647645,128,3250,37,60,1,194,22,"So tena puññakammena devaloke nibbattitvā aparāparaṃ puññāni katvā sugatīsuyeva saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde anantaraṃ vuttassa rādhattherassa kaniṭṭho hutvā nibbatti, surādho tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
647646,128,3250,61,73,1,107,12,So jeṭṭhabhātari rādhe pabbajite sayampi pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
