647862,128,3393,2,8,1,46,5,"Addasaṃ virajaṃ buddhaṃ, lokajeṭṭhaṃ narāsabhaṃ."
647863,128,3394,2,10,1,40,6,"‘ ‘ Pasannacitto sumano, sire katvāna añjaliṃ; "
