648047,128,3501,18,23,1,44,4,{Dhaṅkarūpā}ti kāḷavaṇṇattā eva kākasadisarūpā. 
648048,128,3501,24,31,1,65,6,Satthiñca {bhetvā}ti matasarīrassa satthiṃ jaṇṇubhedanena bhañjitvā. 
648049,128,3501,32,38,1,46,6,Aparañca satthin ti itarañca satthiṃ bhañjitvā. 
648050,128,3501,39,45,1,57,5,Bāhañca {bhetvā}ti bāhaṭṭhiñca aggabāhaṭṭhāneyeva bhañjitvā. 
648051,128,3501,46,64,1,163,16,"Sīsañca bhetvā {dadhithālakaṃvā}ti matasarīrassa sīsaṃ bhinditvā bhinnattā eva leḍḍudaṇḍādīhi paggharantaṃ dadhithālakaṃ viya, paggharantaṃ matthaluṅgaṃ katvāti attho. "
648052,128,3501,65,83,1,159,17,Esā nisinnā {abhisandahitvā}ti chinnabhinnāvayavaṃ matasarīraṃ te avayave yathāṭhāneyeva ṭhapanena sandahitvā sahitaṃ katvā maṃsāpaṇaṃ pasārentī viya esā nisinnā. 
648053,128,3502,2,31,1,245,27,"Yo ve avidvā upadhiṃ {karotī}ti yo imāya upaṭṭhāpitaṃ kammaṭṭhānaṃ disvāpi avidvā akusalo kammaṭṭhānaṃ chaḍḍetvā ayonisomanasikārena kilesūpadhiṃ uppādeti, so mando mandapañño saṃsārassa anativattanato punappunaṃ aparāparaṃ nirayādīsu dukkhaṃ upeti. "
648054,128,3502,32,44,1,63,9,"Tasmā pajānaṃ upadhiṃ na {kayirā}ti {tasmā}ti yasmā cetadevaṃ, tasmā. "
648055,128,3502,45,65,1,114,16,Pajānaṃ upadhin ti‘‘ idha yaṃ dukkhaṃ sambhotī’’ ti pajānanto yoniso manasikaronto kilesūpadhiṃ na kayirā na uppādeyya. 
648056,128,3502,66,67,1,5,1,Kasmā? 
