648726,128,3964,2,4,1,27,2,6 . Puṇṇamāsattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
648727,128,3965,2,9,1,61,6,Pañca nīvaraṇe {hitvā}tiādikā āyasmato puṇṇamāsattherassa gāthā. 
648728,128,3965,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
648729,128,3965,13,52,1,354,37,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto tissassa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ satthari araññe viharante paṃsukūlacīvaraṃ dumasākhāya laggetvā gandhakuṭiṃ paviṭṭhe dhanuhattho gahanaṃ paviṭṭho satthu paṃsukūlaṃ disvā pasannamānaso dhanuṃ nikkhipitvā buddhaguṇe anussaritvā paṃsukūlaṃ vandi. 
648730,128,3965,53,63,1,100,10,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ kuṭumbiyakule nibbatti. 
648731,128,3965,64,74,1,96,10,Tassa kira jātadivase tasmiṃ gehe sabbabhājanāni suvaṇṇaratanamayehi māsehi paripuṇṇāneva ahesuṃ. 
648732,128,3965,75,80,1,36,5,Tenassa puṇṇamāso tveva nāmaṃ akaṃsu. 
648733,128,3965,81,97,1,141,16,So vayappatto dārapariggahaṃ katvā ekasmiṃ putte uppanne gharāvāsaṃ pahāya pabbajitvā gāmakāvāse vasanto ghaṭento vāyamanto chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
