648977,128,4109,2,4,1,24,2,2 . Sivakattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
648978,128,4110,2,9,1,50,5,Aniccāni {gahakānī}ti āyasmato sivakattherassa gāthā. 
648979,128,4110,10,12,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
648980,128,4110,13,39,1,235,26,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni upacinanto vipassissa bhagavato kāle kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ bhagavantaṃ piṇḍāya carantaṃ passitvā pasannamānaso pattaṃ ādāya kummāsassa pūretvā adāsi. 
648981,128,4110,40,55,1,121,14,"So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde rājagahe brāhmaṇakule nibbatti, sivako tissa nāmaṃ ahosi. "
648982,128,4110,56,80,1,240,23,So vayappatto vijjāsippesu nipphattiṃ gato nekkhammajjhāsayatāya kāme pahāya paribbājakapabbajjaṃ pabbajitvā vicaranto satthāraṃ upasaṅkamitvā dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto nacirasseva arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
648983,128,4110,81,94,1,19,3,Tena vuttaṃ apadāne( apa. thera2.56.117-121)–
648984,128,4111,2,9,1,38,5,"‘ ‘ Esanāya carantassa, vipassissa mahesino; "
648985,128,4112,2,9,1,45,6,"Rittakaṃ pattaṃ disvāna, kummāsaṃ pūrayiṃ ahaṃ."
648986,128,4113,2,10,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Ekanavutito kappe, yaṃ bhikkhamadadiṃ tadā; "
648987,128,4114,2,8,1,43,5,"Duggatiṃ nābhijānāmi, kummāsassa idaṃ phalaṃ."
648988,128,4115,2,16,1,51,9,‘ ‘ Kilesā jhāpitā mayhaṃ… pe… kataṃ buddhassa sāsanan’’ ti. 
648989,128,4116,2,7,1,37,5,Arahattaṃ pana patvā aññaṃ byākaronto– 
648990,128,4117,2,4,1,0,0,183.
648991,128,4118,2,10,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Aniccāni gahakāni, tattha tattha punappunaṃ; "
648992,128,4119,2,8,1,42,5,"Gahakāraṃ gavesanto, dukkhā jāti punappunaṃ. "
648993,128,4120,2,4,1,0,0,184.
648994,128,4121,2,11,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Gahakāraka diṭṭhosi, puna gehaṃ na kāhasi; "
648995,128,4122,2,10,1,43,7,"Sabbā te phāsukā bhaggā, thūṇikā ca vidālitā; "
648996,128,4123,2,10,1,45,5,"Vimariyādikataṃ cittaṃ, idheva vidhamissatī’’ ti."
648997,128,4123,11,14,1,18,2,– gāthādvayaṃ abhāsi; 
648998,128,4124,2,22,1,171,19,"Tattha aniccāni gahakāni, tattha tattha punappunan ti tasmiṃ tasmiṃ bhave punappunaṃ nibbattamānāni gahakāni attabhāvagehāni na nibbāni anavaṭṭhitāni ittarāni parittakālāni. "
648999,128,4124,23,35,1,117,11,Gahakāraṃ {gavesanto}ti imassa attabhāvagehassa kārakaṃ taṇhāvaḍḍhakiṃ pariyesanto ettakaṃ kālaṃ anuvicarinti adhippāyo. 
649000,128,4124,36,44,1,66,7,Dukkhā jāti punappunan ti idaṃ gahakārakagavesanassa kāraṇavacanaṃ . 
649001,128,4124,45,66,1,141,18,"Yasmā jarābyādhimaraṇamissatāya jāti nāmesā punappunaṃ upagantuṃ dukkhā, na ca sā tasmiṃ adiṭṭhe nivattati, tasmā taṃ gavesanto vicarinti attho. "
649002,128,4125,2,18,1,104,13,"Gahakāraka {diṭṭhosī}ti idāni pana yena so sakkā daṭṭhuṃ, tena ariyamaggañāṇacakkhunā gahakāraka diṭṭho asi. "
649003,128,4125,19,32,1,92,13,Puna gehan ti puna imasmiṃ saṃsāravaṭṭe attabhāvasaṅkhātaṃ mama gehaṃ na kāhasi na karissasi. 
649004,128,4125,33,43,1,71,9,Sabbā te phāsukā {bhaggā}ti tava sabbā anavasesakilesaphāsukā mayā bhaggā. 
649005,128,4125,44,56,1,93,11,Thūṇikā ca {vidālitā}ti idāni tayā kātabbassa attabhāvagehassa avijjāsaṅkhātā kaṇṇikā ca bhinnā. 
649006,128,4125,57,68,1,89,10,"Vimariyādikataṃ cittan ti mama cittaṃ vigatantaṃ kataṃ, āyatiṃ anuppattidhammataṃ āpāditaṃ. "
649007,128,4125,69,80,1,106,10,"Tato eva idheva vidhamissati imasmiṃyeva bhave viddhaṃsissati, carimakacittanirodhena nirujjhissatīti attho. "
649008,128,4126,2,4,1,33,2,Sivakattheragāthāvaṇṇanā niṭṭhitā.
649009,128,4127,2,4,1,25,2,3 . Upavāṇattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
649010,128,4128,2,8,1,47,5,Arahaṃ {sugato}ti āyasmato upavāṇattherassa gāthā. 
649011,128,4128,9,11,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
649012,128,4128,12,41,1,290,29,Ayaṃ kira padumuttarassa bhagavato kāle daliddakule nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto bhagavati parinibbute tassa dhātuṃ gahetvā manussadevanāgagaruḷakumbhaṇḍayakkhagandhabbehi sattaratanamaye sattayojanike thūpe kate tattha sudhotaṃ attano uttarāsaṅgaṃ veḷagge ābandhitvā dhajaṃ katvā pūjaṃ akāsi. 
649013,128,4128,42,57,1,151,15,Taṃ gahetvā abhisammatako nāma yakkhasenāpati devehi cetiyapūjārakkhaṇatthaṃ ṭhapito adissamānakāyo ākāse dhārento cetiyaṃ tikkhattuṃ padakkhiṇaṃ akāsi. 
649014,128,4128,58,64,1,48,6,So taṃ disvā bhiyyosomattāya pasannamānaso ahosi. 
649015,128,4128,65,91,1,264,25,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde sāvatthiyaṃ brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {upavāṇo}ti laddhanāmo vayappatto jetavanapaṭiggahaṇe buddhānubhāvaṃ disvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto arahattaṃ patvā chaḷabhiñño ahosi. 
