649175,128,4266,11,13,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
649176,128,4266,14,40,1,249,26,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni karonto ito catunavutikappamatthake kulagehe nibbattitvā viññutaṃ patto ekadivasaṃ sataraṃsiṃ nāma paccekabuddhaṃ nirodhā vuṭṭhahitvā piṇḍāya carantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso tālaphalaṃ adāsi. 
649177,128,4266,41,62,1,172,16,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde magadharaṭṭhe gahapatikule nibbattitvā‘‘ sambulo’’ ti laddhanāmo kaccānagottatāya {sambulakaccāno}ti paññāyittha. 
649178,128,4267,2,18,1,152,16,So vayappatto satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā himavantasamīpe bheravāya nāma pabbataguhāyaṃ vipassanāya kammaṃ karonto viharati. 
