649207,128,4288,2,4,1,24,2,6 . Nitakattheragāthāvaṇṇanā 
649208,128,4289,2,11,1,56,7,Kassa selūpamaṃ cittan ti āyasmato nitakattherassa gāthā. 
649209,128,4289,12,14,1,10,2,Kā uppatti? 
649210,128,4289,15,39,1,230,24,Ayampi purimabuddhesu katādhikāro tattha tattha bhave puññāni karonto vipassissa bhagavato kāle bandhumatīnagare ārāmagopako hutvā jīvanto ekadivasaṃ bhagavantaṃ ākāsena gacchantaṃ disvā pasannamānaso nāḷikeraphalaṃ dātukāmo ahosi. 
649211,128,4289,40,46,1,51,6,Satthā taṃ anuggaṇhanto ākāseyeva ṭhatvā paṭiggaṇhi. 
649212,128,4289,47,53,1,46,6,So taṃ datvā uḷāraṃ pītisomanassaṃ paṭisaṃvedi. 
649213,128,4289,54,82,1,259,27,So tena puññakammena devamanussesu saṃsaranto imasmiṃ buddhuppāde kosalaraṭṭhe brāhmaṇakule nibbattitvā {nitako}ti laddhanāmo viññutaṃ patto satthu santike dhammaṃ sutvā paṭiladdhasaddho pabbajitvā kammaṭṭhānaṃ gahetvā araññe viharanto ghaṭento arahattaṃ pāpuṇi. 
