649229,128,4304,2,35,1,256,25,"191. Tattha kassa selūpamaṃ cittaṃ, ṭhitaṃ {nānupakampatī}ti imasmiṃ araññāyatane vasantesu kassa bhikkhuno cittaṃ aggaphalādhigamena ekaghanasilāmayapabbatūpamaṃ sabbesaṃ iñjanānaṃ abhāvato vasībhāvappattiyā ca ṭhitaṃ sabbehipi lokadhammehi nānukampati na vedhati. "
