649321,128,4356,2,10,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Hatthikkhandhato oruyha, saṃvegaṃ alabhiṃ tadā; "
649322,128,4357,2,13,1,46,8,"Sohaṃ ditto tadā santo, patto me āsavakkhayo’’ ti."
